22General%20Dhiraj%20Seth%20set%20to%20take%20over%20as%20the%2031st%20Chief%20of%20the%20Army%20Staff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782795882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-47529300.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fdefence%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-dhiraj-seth-set-to-take-over-as-the-31st-chief-of-the-army-staff%2Farticleshow%2F132084292.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22General%20Dhiraj%20Seth%20set%20to%20assume%20command%20as%20the%20Army's%2031st%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20succeeding%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi.%20A%20distinguished%20Armoured%20Corps%20officer%2C%20General%20Seth%20brings%20extensive%20command%20experience%20from%20Southern%20and%20South%20Western%20Commands%2C%20and%20has%20overseen%20crucial%20staff%20roles%20in%20modernization.%20His%20tenure%20is%20set%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20army's%20'decade%20of%20transformation%2C'%20including%20integrated%20battle%20groups%20and%20drone%20integration%2C%20aiming%20to%20enhance%20inter-service%20coordination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22DHRUV%20YADAV%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20oil%20market%20has%20moved%20from%20fearing%20shortages%20to%20pricing%20in%20a%20very%20different%20future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224898%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gas%20pump%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a433126a25092c74cca12a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223266%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWall%20Street%20is%20turning%20more%20bearish%20on%20oil%20as%20supply%20rebounds%20and%20demand%20worries%20persist.%3Cp%3EAdam%20J.%20Dewey%2FAnadolu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGlobal%20oil%20supply%20is%20rebounding%20faster%20than%20expected%2C%20easing%20crude%20shortage%20fears.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrent%20crude%20has%20tumbled%20from%20%24126%20to%20%2473%20as%20Gulf%20producers%20ramp%20up%20output.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWall%20Street%20is%20cutting%20oil%20price%20forecasts%20as%20supply%20recovers%20and%20demand%20softens.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oil%20market%20has%20gone%20from%20fearing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-surges-after-trump-triumphant-speech-on-iran-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20shock%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20worrying%20about%20too%20much%20crude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrent%20crude%20oil%20futures%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20trading%20around%20%2473%20a%20barrel%20early%20on%20Tuesday.%20That%20is%20roughly%20back%20to%20prewar%20levels%20after%20topping%20%24126%20in%20April%20as%20the%20Iran%20conflict%20stoked%20fears%20of%20a%20major%20disruption%20to%20global%20oil%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20price%20collapse%20is%20simple%3A%20Supply%20is%20recovering%20faster%20than%20expected%20in%20a%20market%20that%20was%20already%20facing%20demand%20concerns%20before%20the%20latest%20selloff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20growing%20expectation%20that%20the%20global%20oil%20market%20will%20be%20well%20supplied%20through%202027%2C%26quot%3B%20Warren%20Patterson%2C%20ING's%20head%20of%20commodities%20strategy%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatterson%20said%20oil%20near%20%2470%20a%20barrel%20had%20%26quot%3Bclose%20to%20zero%20geopolitical%20risk%20premium%26quot%3B%20priced%20in.%20Expectations%20of%20a%202027%20surplus%20would%20weigh%20on%20sentiment%20because%20markets%20are%20forward-looking%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20preliminary%20US-Iran%20agreement%20or%20the%20pickup%20in%20tanker%20traffic%20through%20the%20vital%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-iran-switzerland-talks-called-off-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20a%20quarter%20of%20global%20seaborne%20oil%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERystad%20Energy%20estimated%20that%20about%202%20million%20barrels%20a%20day%20of%20oil%20production%20had%20been%20restored%20across%20the%20Gulf%20over%20the%20past%20three%20weeks%20as%20producers%20brought%20fields%20back%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20supply%20picture%20is%20clearly%20improving%2C%26quot%3B%20Aditya%20Saraswat%2C%20Rystad's%20MENA%20research%20director%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShipments%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Kuwait%20are%20also%20showing%20signs%20of%20recovery.%20Rystad%20said%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20on%20track%20for%20record%20exports%20through%20its%20Red%20Sea%20terminal%20at%20Yanbu%2C%20while%20Kuwait%20has%20lifted%20force%20majeure%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERystad%20now%20expects%20regional%20production%20to%20return%20to%20pre-conflict%20levels%20by%20December%2C%20rather%20than%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20faster%20recovery%20is%20prompting%20Wall%20Street%20to%20rethink%20oil's%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20cut%20its%20fourth-quarter%202026%20Brent%20forecast%20from%20%2490%20to%20%2480%20a%20barrel%20and%20lowered%20its%202027%20average%20forecast%20from%20%2480%20to%20%2475%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20has%20also%20lowered%20its%20Brent%20forecasts%2C%20cutting%20its%20outlook%20from%20%2485%20to%20%2480%20a%20barrel%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20through%202027.%20JPMorgan%20also%20expects%20Brent%20to%20average%20%2480%20a%20barrel%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20and%20extend%20its%20decline%20to%20average%20%2464%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20supply%20is%20not%20the%20only%20reason%20Wall%20Street%20is%20turning%20more%20bearish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Goldman%20warned%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-demand-not-supply-risk-goldman-sachs-forecast-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweaker%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20major%20downside%20risk%20for%20crude%2C%20pointing%20to%20softer%20fuel%20consumption%20in%20China%20and%20parts%20of%20Europe.%20The%20bank%20also%20sees%20a%20longer-term%20demand%20risk%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-oil-prices-iran-war-electric-vehicles-gas-prices-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20remains%20a%20key%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERystad%20said%20Gulf%20storage%20tanks%20were%20about%2050%25%20to%2060%25%20full%2C%20giving%20producers%20only%20a%20limited%20buffer%20if%20tanker%20traffic%20fails%20to%20normalize.%20If%20flows%20through%20the%20strait%20do%20not%20pick%20up%2C%20producers%20may%20have%20to%20throttle%20output%20again%2C%20pushing%20the%20full%20recovery%20into%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20diplomatic%20agreement%20is%20a%20necessary%20first%20step%20and%20physical%20tanker%20flows%20through%20Hormuz%20are%20what%20we%20are%20watching%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Saraswat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrude-oil-prices-today-supply-demand-outlook-forecast-hormuz-exports-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782795817000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a433154360acd489560d3f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrude-oil-prices-today-supply-demand-outlook-forecast-hormuz-exports-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Global%20oil%20supply%20recovery%20eases%20shortage%20fears%20as%20Brent%20crude%20falls%20to%20%2473.%20Wall%20Street%20is%20lowering%20forecasts%20amid%20demand%20concerns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huilen