ening-k-shaped-economy-research-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20prices%20immediately%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20are%20too%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20gauging%2C%20which%20is%20totally%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20likely%20referring%20to%20gouging%2C%20the%20act%20of%20overcharging%20customers.%20%26quot%3BIf%20retailers%20don't%20do%20this%2C%20big%20problems%20lie%20ahead!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20retailers%20should%20%26quot%3Bstart%20targeting%20around%20the%20%242.50%20a%20gallon%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20California%20should%20stop%20charging%20heavy%20taxes%20on%20its%20gasoline.%20The%20state%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20the%20gas%20tax%20rate%20from%2061.4%20cents%20per%20gallon%20to%2063.4%20cents%20per%20gallon%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Monday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-high-how-to-save-money-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaverage%20gas%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20nationwide%20stood%20at%20%243.86%20per%20gallon%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20American%20Automobile%20Association.%20California%20and%20Hawaii%20currently%20have%20the%20highest%20gas%20prices%20in%20the%20country%2C%20at%20%245.45%20and%20%245.49%20per%20gallon%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20Truth%20Social%20post%20comes%20about%20a%20week%20after%20he%20slammed%20big%20oil%20companies%20for%20keeping%20oil%20prices%20high%20despite%20easing%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20Oil%20Companies%20are%20not%20dropping%20their%20price%20at%20the%20pump%20commensurate%20with%20the%20sharply%20lower%20prices%20they%20are%20paying%20for%20Oil.%20Those%20prices%20are%20dropping%20like%20a%20rock!%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20had%20instructed%20the%20Justice%20Department%20to%20investigate%20oil%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChevron's%20finance%20chief%20Eimear%20Bonner%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Thursday%20that%20energy%20providers%20were%20doing%20what%20they%20could%2C%20but%20it%20would%20take%20time%20for%20prices%20to%20come%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20take%20time%2C%20though.%20There%20is%20a%20lag%20between%2C%20you%20know%2C%20oil%20prices%20and%20reductions%20in%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20when%20that%20shows%20up%20at%20the%20pump%2C%20but%20we%20expect%20that%20prices%20will%20come%20down%20as%20things%20continue%20to%20normalize%2C%26quot%3B%20Bonner%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGas%20prices%20have%20skyrocketed%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20US-Iran%20war%20in%20February%2C%20with%20the%20nationwide%20average%20climbing%20to%20well%20above%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-drop-below-4-gallon-first-time-in-months-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%244%20per%20gallon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20the%20AAA.%20They%20have%20come%20down%20slightly%20after%20peace%20talks%20with%20Iran%20were%20initiated%2C%20and%20after%20Trump%20announced%20a%20ceasefire%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-gas-companies-must-lower-prices-warning-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782793185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4324c3e218c3b62535f07b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-gas-companies-must-lower-prices-warning-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20nationwide%20gas%20price%20stood%20at%20%243.86%20per%20gallon%20as%20of%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AAA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22She%20has%20one%20of%20the%20rarest%20jobs%20in%20nerd%20business%3A%20lore%20keeper.%20She%20doesn't%20think%20AI%20will%20replace%20her.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223924%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Skye%20Smith%20wearing%20sunglasses%20poses%20beside%20a%20gold%20lion%20statue%20under%20an%20illuminated%20MGM%20GRAND%20GARDEN%20ARENA%20wall%20sign.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3cb144360acd489560ac1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESkye%20Smith%20is%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020's%26quot%3B%20lorekeeper%20and%20game%20master%20Brennan%20Lee%20Mulligan's%20right-hand.%3Cp%3EDropout%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBrennan%20Lee%20Mulligan%20is%20the%20most%20famous%20face%20from%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20weave%20fantasy%20worlds%20without%20his%20assistant%2C%20Skye%20Smith.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESmith%20told%20us%20what%20she%20does%20at%20work%2C%20creating%20the%20role-playing%20game%20live%20show%20that%20took%20over%20Madison%20Square%20Garden.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20stadium%20lights%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-dimension-20-dropout-built-nerdworld-empire-madison-square-garden-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadison%20Square%20Garden%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20cheered%20for%20Brennan%20Lee%20Mulligan%2C%20the%20game%20master%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdimension-20-plans-comic-us-tour-madison-square-garden-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimension%2020%26quot%3B%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20tabletop%20roleplaying%20game%20show's%20most%20famous%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%2C%20run%20by%20Dropout%20%E2%80%94%20a%20media%20company%20spun%20off%20from%20the%20former%20CollegeHumor%20%E2%80%94%20involves%20Mulligan%20or%20other%20game%20masters%20weaving%20a%20fantastical%20tale%20of%20adventure%20and%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMulligan%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%20hours%20long%20games%2C%20at%20stadiums%20and%20in%20the%20show's%20recorded%20form%20without%20Skye%20Smith%2C%20his%20lore%20keeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Business%20Insider%20asked%20Smith%20to%20sum%20up%20her%20work%2C%20she%20described%20herself%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BGoogle%2C%20or%20Wikipedia%2C%20for%20'Dimension%2020.'%26quot%3B%20She's%20in%20charge%20of%20knowing%20the%20show's%20encyclopedic%2C%20sprawling%20history%2C%20from%20timelines%20to%20factoids%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20her%20boss%20and%20his%20players%20keep%20it%20all%20straight%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235a78d00-3bae-45e5-81d2-436022ff361a%5C%22%3EThe%20game%20master's%20right-hand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShows%20like%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-mercer-brennan-lee-mulligan-critical-role-dimension-20-collaboration-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20need%20lore%20keepers%20for%20one%20reason%3A%20There's%20just%20too%20much%20to%20remember.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-cco-matt-mercer-top-tip-cope-with-burnout-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20streamed%20multi-year%20tabletop%20games%20for%20hundreds%20of%20episodes%2C%20totaling%20thousands%20of%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020%26quot%3B%20has%20shorter%20seasons%2C%20the%20game%20master%20leans%20on%20an%20assistant%20to%20ensure%20he%20gets%20the%20plot%20points%20and%20facts%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20filming%20day%20for%20me%20is%20very%20different%20than%20a%20regular%2010-to-6%20workday.%20It's%20always%20going%20to%20be%20at%20least%20a%2012-hour%20workday.%20I%20get%20to%20set%20the%20same%20time%20as%20our%20GM%2C%20Brennan.%20And%20then%20I%20stay%20until%20pretty%20much%20the%20very%20last%20person%20has%20left%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDimension%2020%26quot%3B%20films%20multiple%20episodes%20a%20day%2C%20and%20she%20and%20Mulligan%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20Slack%26quot%3B%20going%20as%20they%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20takes%20notes%20on%20the%20ongoing%20game%2C%20then%20fields%20questions%20called%20to%20her%20off-camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed0e7710-5844-48da-a6fc-02d6e11e2f2c%5C%22%3EStaying%20organized%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20track%20of%20evolving%20lore%2C%20Smith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairtables-ceo-wants-staff-take-time-off-work-play-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euses%20Airtable%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20most%20of%20her%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20uses%20some%20good%20old-fashioned%20sticky%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20usually%20have%20a%20printout%20of%20either%20the%20materials%20that%20they%20use%20at%20the%20table%20for%20the%20game%20that%20we%20play%2C%20or%20a%20visual%20of%20the%20world%20we're%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20always%20have%20a%20notebook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20lorekeeping%2C%20Smith%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20creative%20process%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdimension-20-new-season-misfits-and-magic-aabria-iyengar-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDimension%2020's%26quot%3B%20new%20seasons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20pitching%20and%20ideation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20get%20to%20know%20what's%20cooking%20really%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22548ca9cc-910e-4f7e-9a50-b4a3f84f14a9%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20question%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20her%20job%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-no-ai-legend-of-vox-machina-fourth-season-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eendangered%20by%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20note-takers%2C%20Smith%20said%20that%20her%20work%20revolves%20around%20listening%2C%20spotting%20human%20error%2C%20and%20understanding%20the%20lore%20of%20the%20fantasy%20world%20being%20made%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20big%20part%20of%20this%20job%20and%20why%20it's%20important%20has%20to%20do%20with%20human%20error%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20And%20so%20fixing%20'errors'%20with%20a%20machine%20would%20never%20work%20because%20what%20you%20need%20is%20another%20human%20set%20of%20eyes%20who%20knows%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20making%20something%20creative%2C%20knows%20where%20the%20weak%20spots%20are%2C%20and%20you%20just%20can't%20train%20an%20electronic%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20you%20can%20train%20human%20intuition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20added%20that%20she%20enjoys%20the%20%26quot%3Bhard%20parts%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20job%20that%20other%20people%20might%20find%20taxing%20or%20that%20they%20might%20look%20to%20robots%20to%20help%20with%2C%20such%20as%20taking%20%26quot%3Bhours%20and%20hours%20of%20notes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20double-layered%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20never%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%20as%20well%20as%20I%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20given%20the%20environmental%20effects%20of%20AI%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20even%20be%20worth%20it%20to%20try.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219b65c26-c664-45cb-80f2-fd56d31d372b%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20get%20the%20gig%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20worked%20her%20way%20up%20to%20lore%20keeper%20from%20an%20entry-level%20role%20as%20a%20production%20assistant%20in%202023%2C%20then%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20work%20on%20%26quot%3BDimension%2020%26quot%3B%20when%20Dropout%20offered%20her%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20career%20highlights%20include%20w