ith%20our%20daughter%2C%20because%20this%20is%20her%20new%20reality%2C%20you%20know%3F%26quot%3B%20Turner-Smith%20told%20podcast%20host%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoda-kotb-former-boss-body-shamed-her-at-work-harassment-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHoda%20Kotb%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BQueen%20and%20Slim%26quot%3B%20star%20said%20they're%20learning%20as%20they%20go%20along%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20the%20idea%20is%20always%20two%20homes%20filled%20with%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20you've%20got%20two%20houses%2C%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20Turner-Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20her%20daughter%20was%20very%20young%20when%20she%20and%20Jackson%20split%2C%20Turner-Smith%20said%20that%20explaining%20the%20separation%20has%20been%20more%20difficult%20than%20dealing%20with%20other%20people's%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20walk%20this%20line%20between%20obviously%20being%20age-appropriate%20and%20child-centered%20in%20the%20way%20that%20you%20talk%20about%20it%2C%20but%20also%20keeping%20it%20real%20so%20that%20she%20has%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20this%20means%2C%26quot%3B%20Turner-Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20my%20favorite%20tool%20in%20all%20of%20this%20has%20been%20my%20favorite%20tool%20for%20life%3A%20books.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20read%20her%20daughter%20%26quot%3Bso%20many%20books%20about%20divorce%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20what%20that%20can%20look%20like%2C%20she%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChildren's%20books%20have%20been%20helpful%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Turner-Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurner-Smith%20isn't%20the%20only%20Hollywood%20celebrity%20to%20have%20spoken%20about%20navigating%20divorce%20with%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjason-travis-kelce-parents-donna-postponed-divorce-after-college-nfl-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDo