igcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2Fsinger%20appeared%20in%20a%20ton%20of%20Swift's%20Instagram%20posts%20in%20the%20pre-2015%20%26quot%3Bsquad%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBad%20Blood%26quot%3B%20video%2C%20and%20even%20walked%20onstage%20during%20one%20of%20the%20famous%20%26quot%3Bsquad%26quot%3B%20appearances%20from%20the%201989%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Steinfeld%20was%20best%20known%20for%20her%20roles%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BPitch%20Perfect%26quot%3B%20series%20and%20budding%20music%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESteinfeld%20hasn't%20been%20seen%20with%20Swift%20much%20in%20recent%20years.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hailee%20steinfeld%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e503cd2a9f40c1ac21e5008%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22923%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDimitrios%20Kambouris%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESteinfeld%20told%20Seventeen%20magazine%20in%202016%20that%20she%20didn't%20spend%20as%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seventeen.com%2Fcelebrity%2Fa42053%2Fhailee-steinfeld-seventeen-september-2016-cover%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20with%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20people%20might%20have%20assumed%2C%20but%20that%20she%20does%20consider%20her%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fhailee-steinfeld-digital-cover-people-may-7499889%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20People%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20will%20always%20%26quot%3Brun%20to%20the%20phone%26quot%3B%20whenever%20Swift%20calls.%20When%20Steinfeld%20posted%20on%20Instagram%20about%20her%20engagement%20to%20athlete%20Josh%20Allen%20in%202024%2C%20Swift%20liked%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESwift%20had%20Ellie%20Goulding%20perform%20with%20her%20during%20the%201989%20tour.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22