%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Swift%20reportedly%20met%20at%20the%20Young%20Hollywood%20Awards%20in%202008%20and%20became%20fast%20friends.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Stone%20had%20already%20been%20in%20the%20hit%20comedy%20%26quot%3BSuperbad%26quot%3B%20(2007)%20and%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20the%20A-list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStone%20even%20brought%20Swift%20as%20her%20date%20to%20the%202010%20premiere%20of%20her%20movie%20%26quot%3BEasy%20A.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStone%20still%20seems%20to%20be%20one%20of%20Swift's%20most%20low-key%20friends.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223933%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22emma%20stone.JPG%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e504838a9f40c13fe2f5412%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPHIL%20MCCARTEN%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Stone%20doesn't%20have%20Instagram%20and%20didn't%20appear%20in%20many%20of%20the%20Swift%20%26quot%3Bsquad%26quot%3B%20photos%20from%20the%202015-2016%20era%2C%20she%20seems%20to%20still%20be%20acquainted%20with%20the%20singer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStone%20attended%20the%20Reputation%20tour%20in%20New%20Jersey%20in%20July%202018%2C%20and%20the%20actor%20was%20spotted%20at%20Swift's%20Eras%20Tour%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Few.com%2Fmusic%2Ftaylor-swift-when-emma-falls-in-love-emma-stone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFans%20have%20also%20speculated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Swift's%20%26quot%3BSpeak%20Now%20(Taylor's%20Version)%26quot%3B%20vault%20track%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Emma%20Falls%20in%20Love%26quot%3B%20is%20about%20Stone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStone%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Fpop%2Femma-stone-credit-taylor-swift-florida-1235661270%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredited%20on%20Swift's%20song%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BFlorida!!!%20(feat.%20Florence%20%2B%20The%20Machine)%26quot%3B%20on%20%26quot%3BTh