%3BFolklore%26quot%3B%20in%20July%202020%2C%20Swift%20gifted%20Berard%20the%20cardigan%20from%20the%20album's%20merch%2C%20and%20Berard%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20herself%20wearing%20it%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20caption%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BTaylor.%20Swift.%20What%20an%20absolute%20wonder%20you%20are.%20Your%20lyrical%20ability%20to%20move%20us%20is%20seismic.%20Much%20like%20this%20beautiful%20gifted%20cardigan%2C%20this%20album%20is%20a%20dream.%20I've%20never%20been%20more%20appreciative%20of%20your%20art.%20This%20one%20did%20something%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Berard%20attended%20the%20second%20Nashville%20show%20on%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Fmusic-news%2Ftaylor-swift-fifteen-abigail-reaction-nashville-1235323426%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwift%20dedicated%20%26quot%3BFifteen%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20her.%20The%20longtime%20friend%20even%20showed%20up%20on%20the%20Spotify%20canvas%20for%20%26quot%3BNew%20Romantics%26quot%3B%20on%20Swift's%20%26quot%3B1989%20(Taylor's%20Version).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20also%20seemed%20to%20write%20about%20Berard%20once%20more%20in%20her%20recent%20song%20%26quot%3BRuin%20the%20Friendship%26quot%3B%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Life%20of%20a%20Showgirl.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERuby%20Rose%20and%20Swift%20met%20around%202015.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GettyImages%20518809096%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e54371fa9f40c279b74dd93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221794%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Kempin%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20GLAAD%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20had%20been%20acting%20and%20DJing%20in%20Australia%20for%20many%20years%2C%20Ruby%20Rose%20got%20her%20big%20break%20in%20the%20US%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20cast%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3