%20about%20the%20singer%20in%20college%20had%20the%20%26quot%3BRed%26quot%3B%20album%20existed%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20responded%20and%20said%20she%20loved%20Dunham's%20HBO%20show%20%26quot%3BGirls%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20Dunham%20supposedly%20sent%20her%20a%20DM%20saying%20she%20was%20excited%20to%20become%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20two%20met%20in%20person%20at%20the%20Grammys.%20In%202015%2C%20Dunham%20appeared%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBad%20Blood%26quot%3B%20music%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDunham%20still%20seems%20to%20view%20Swift%20in%20high%20regard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222854%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lena%20Dunham%20being%20hugged%20by%20Taylor%20Swift%20in%202015%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42dcd8360acd489560d2f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222141%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELena%20Dunham%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20in%202015.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Kravitz%2FFilmMagic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDunham%20attended%20Swift's%20Reputation%20tour%20in%202018%20and%20told%20The%20Cut%20in%20November%20of%20that%20year%20that%20even%20she%20was%20surprised%20to%20still%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecut.com%2F2018%2F11%2Flena-dunham-comes-to-terms-with-herself.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efriends%20with%20the%20superstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDunham%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2Ftelevision%2F8479457%2Flena-dunham-taylor-swift-politics-ex-boyfriends-wwhl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowed%20her%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Swift%20in%202018%20after%20the%20singer%20publicly%20endorsed%20two%20Democratic%20candidates%20in%20Tennessee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20she%20praised%20Swift%20on%20Instagram%20for%20her%20%26quot%3BME!%26quot%3B%20music%20video%20and%20posted%20a%20heartfelt%20message%20for%20Swift's%2030th%20birthday%20later%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp