r's%20Peter%20Kafka%3C%2Fa%3E%20writes%2C%20what%20once%20sounded%20like%20a%20good%20idea%E2%80%94the%20company%20that%20sells%20you%20your%20cable%20and%20internet%20also%20making%20shows%20and%20movies%E2%80%94now%20seems%20less%20so%2C%20and%20the%20spinoff%20is%20an%20acknowledgment%20that%20these%20businesses%20are%20more%20valuable%20apart%20than%20tied%20up%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20clear%20that%20our%20technology%20and%20media%20businesses%20each%20have%20compelling%20opportunities%20in%20front%20of%20them%20that%20are%20distinct%20in%20nature%20and%20best%20pursued%20with%20dedicated%20focus%2C%20strategic%20flexibility%2C%20and%20tailored%20investment%20priorities%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Roberts%2C%20Comcast's%20co-CEO%2C%20said%20during%20a%20conference%20call%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20some%20top%20commentators%20in%20business%20and%20markets%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20news.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275c0341c-762b-498c-8b34-6e1012282aef%5C%22%3EPaul%20Nary%2C%20professor%20at%20the%20Wharton%20School%20of%20Business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENary%20said%20the%20deal%20could%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20coming%20merger%20or%20acquisition%20with%20another%20media%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20split%20makes%20sense%2C%20leads%20to%20creation%20of%20two%20more%20focused%2C%20hopefully%20more%20profitable%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%2C%20until%20the%20next%20opportunity%20for%20a%20media%20megamerger%20presents%20itself.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20guarantee%20the%20big%20industry%20players%20are%20already%20considering%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20deal%20to%20be%20made%20there%20in%20pursuit%20of%20building%20an%20ever-bigger%20empire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f16ef71a-f610-4d10-8863-cc9819544e10%5C%22%3EJeff%20Barrington%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Windsor%20Drake%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBarrington%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20spinoff%20could%20spur%20other%20media%20giants%20to%20break%20themselves%20up%2C%20given%20that%20investors%20rewarded%20the%20move%20after%20it%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20broader%20market%2C%20it's%20the%20clearest%20sign%20yet%20of%20the%202026%20conglomerate%20breakup%20wave%2C%20focus%20is%20finally%20worth%20more%20than%20scale%2C%20and%20a%2020%25%20bounce%20on%20a%20deal%20this%20size%20puts%20every%20sprawling%20media%20and%20telecom%20giant%20on%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8529904-79e3-4cd0-9260-f56536f55c07%5C%22%3ERoss%20Gerber%2C%20CEO%20of%20Gerber%20Kawasaki%20Wealth%20and%20Investment%20Management%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGerber%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Babout%20time%26quot%3B%20the%20move%20happened%2C%20and%20that%20Disney%20should%20follow%20suit%20with%20ESPN%20and%20ABC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20path%20Disney%20needs%20to%20take%20as%20shareholders%20have%20suffered%20long%20enough%20and%20the%20assets%20are%20worth%20more%20apart%20than%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201fbbc51-9eaf-4e2d-828f-40ae6360ed9a%5C%22%3EBrandon%20Katz%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Clarion%20Capital%20Partners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Nary%2C%20Katz%20also%20pointed%20to%20potential%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Comcast%2FNBCU%20split%20makes%20M%26amp%3BA%20even%20easier%20moving%20forward.%20Cleaner%2C%20smaller%20balance%20sheets%20~15%20years%20after%20unified%20scale%20was%20all%20the%20rage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BContent%20hasn't%20moved%20the%20shareholder%20needle%20for%20companies%20where%20it%20isn't%20the%20core%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomcast-nbc-sky-spinoff-stock-market-reaction-commentary-media-cmcsa-202