reamers%2Ffaze-lacy-leaves-core-just-two-months-after-launch-reveals-real-reason-behind-exit%2Famp_articleshow%2F132078625.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Ffaze-lacy-leaves-core-just-two-months-after-launch-reveals-real-reason-behind-exit%2Famp_articleshow%2F132078625.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Best%20dog%20earmuffs%20for%20fireworks%20and%20noise%20anxiety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20photo%20shows%20a%20dog%20resting%20on%20a%20bed%20while%20wearing%20two%20different%20ear%20coverings%3A%20a%20purple%20fabric%20headband%20in%20the%20left%20image%20and%20a%20gray%20padded%20earmuff-style%20hood%20in%20the%20right%20image.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a429ea8e218c3b62535eccf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20reporter's%20dog%20napped%20after%20she%20became%20comfortable%20wearing%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20calming%20band%20and%20Pawnix%20headphones.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Fourth%20of%20July%2C%20my%20family%20travels%20to%20the%20Adirondacks%2C%20where%20revelers%20enjoy%20setting%20off%20fireworks%20all%20weekend.%20We%20used%20to%20love%20watching%20these%20displays%20over%20the%20lake%2C%20but%20since%20adopting%20our%20noise-averse%20pup%2C%20Olive%2C%20we've%20become%20focused%20on%20helping%20her%20cope%20with%20the%20sudden%20pops%2C%20hisses%2C%20and%20booms%20that%20punctuate%20the%20holiday.%20Determined%20to%20ease%20Olive's%20noise%20anxiety%2C%20I%20consulted%20trainers%2C%20behaviorists%2C%20and%20even%20a%20sound%20expert.%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20whether%20ear%20protection%20might%20help%20and%2C%20if%20so%2C%20how%20to%20identify%20the%20best%20dog%20earmuffs%20for%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20preparation%20for%20the%20Fourth%2C%20I've%20been%20testing%20four%20dog%20earmuffs%20with%20Olive.%20Since%20sporadic%20fireworks%20are%20already%20going%20off%2C%20I've%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20try%20some%20of%20these%20tools%20for%20short%20bursts.%20I'll%20have%20a%20full%20evaluation%20after%20the%20Fourth%20and%20will%20report%20back%20with%20our%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a37a9e0a-1dde-4f8c-ae35-58433970b66a%5C%22%3EA%20quick%20look%20at%20the%20best%20dog%20earmuffs%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHappy%20Hoodie%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126761019mrf-20%26h%3Dba230d4b6ef98849b8334001229939b2d85b00ec21827c3735c1105a68f71b63%26postID%3D6a426c82778476c08ad2f971%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-earmuffs%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fhappy-hoodie-calming-cap-dogs%252Fdp%252F239669%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2410-%2414%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20fabric%20%26quot%3Bsnood%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20dogs%20who%20are%20new%20to%20ear%20protection%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20soft%20fabric%20and%20snug%20yet%20comfy%20fit.%20The%20Happy%20Hoodie%20provides%20gentle%20compression%2C%20which%20may%20have%20a%20calming%20effect%20on%20some%20dogs%20and%20seemed%20to%20relax%20my%20own%20dog%20when%20she%20wore%20it%20during%20a%20panic%20episode%20on%20a%20long%20car%20ride.%20Realistically%2C%20the%20fabric%20design%20won't%20block%20out%20very%20loud%20booms%2C%20but%20it%20should%20minimize%20the%20sound%20of%20low%20rumbles%20and%20hairdryers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPawnix%20Noise-Canceling%20Headphones%20for%20Dogs%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpawnix.com%2Fcollections%2Fcatalog%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%24200%20at%20Pawnix%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20These%20earmuffs%20offer%20more%20than%20passive%20noise%20reduction%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20a%20physical%20barrier%20to%20block%20sound%3B%20they%20also%20integrate%20active%20noise%20control%20(ANC)%20technology.%20While%20ANC%20won't%20block%20sudden%20fireworks%20or%20thunder%2C%20it%20could%20help%20with%20other%20ongoing%20noise%20that%20your%20dog%20finds%20bothersome%2C%20like%20traffic%20or%20a%20humming%20air%20conditioner.%20These%20headphones%20can%20also%20mask%20stressful%20sounds%20by%20connecting%20to%20your%20device%20via%20Bluetooth%20and%20playing%20soothing%20music.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDog%20guardians%20should%20temper%20their%20expectations%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20gear.%20Research%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20earmuffs%20is%20limited%2C%20and%20arguments%20in%20their%20favor%20are%20largely%20anecdotal.%20The%20experts%20I%20consulted%20also%20emphasized%20that%20earmuffs%20are%20not%20a%20realistic%20stand-alone%20solution.%20They%20should%20be%20used%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10705068%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroader%20management%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20may%20include%20desensitization%20training%2C%20medication%2C%20and%20environmental%20modifications%20such%20as%20closing%20windows%2C%20playing%20background%20music%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20dogs%20to%20retreat%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20earmuffs%20I%20tested%20have%20limited%20ability%20to%20block%20sound%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feileenanddogs.com%2Fblog%2F2026%2F05%2F16%2Fmost-important-thing-to-know-about-ear-protection-for-dogs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-frequency%20sounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20thunder%20and%20fireworks%2C%20two%20options%20stood%20out%20as%20promising.%20Each%20one%20has%20unique%20strengths%20that%20make%20them%20well-suited%20to%20different%20dogs%20and%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286032246-fdc4-4656-96ce-d195b5b5ff8a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20dog%20earmuffs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dog%2C%20Olive%2C%20is%20petrified%20of%20fireworks.%20All%20it%20takes%20is%20one%20unexpected%20boom%20to%20send%20her%20fleeing%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20where%20she%20trembles%20and%20pants%20for%20hours.%20It's%20heartbreaking.%20This%20inspired%20me%20to%20find%20the%20best%20dog%20earmuffs%20by%20evaluating%20their%20performance%20in%20several%20key%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20did%20my%20best%20to%20simulate%20real-world%20conditions%2C%20I%20should%20acknowledge%20the%20inherent%20limitations%20of%20my%20methodology.%20For%20one%2C%20there%20are%20some%20things%20I%20just%20couldn't%20replicate%2C%20like%20the%20change%20in%20barometric%20pressure%20during%20a%20thunderstorm%2C%20or%20the%20bone-rattling%20sensation%20of%20nearby%20fireworks.%20I%20also%20can't%20get%20in%20Olive's%20head%3B%20I%20can't%20actually%20hear%20what%20she%20hears.%20With%20these%20restraints%20in%20mind%2C%20here's%20how%20I%20landed%20on%20my%20top%20picks%20for%20dog%20ear%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20was%20the%20top%20priority%20in%20my%20evaluations.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20else%20matters%20if%20the%20dog%20is%20miserable%20when%20the%20ear%20protection%20is%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccpdt.org%2Fdog-owners%2Fcertified-dog-trainer-directory%2Fprofile%2F2196127%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmanda%20Farah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20professional%20dog%20trainer%20and%20national%20training%20and%20behavior%20coordinator%20at%20Best%20Friends%20Animal%20Society.%20I%20weighed%20each%20earmuff%2C%20awarding%20higher%20scores%20to%20those%20that%20weighed%20less.%20Then%20I%20held%20the%20fabric%20against%20my%20skin%20and%20checked%20for%20any%20scratchiness%20or%20rough%20stitching.%20Finally%2C%20I%20observed%20Olive's%20response%20while%20she%20wore%20each%20earmuff%2C%20noting%20whether%20she%20pawed%20at%20it%20or%20appeared%20distressed%20with%20it%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlexandra%20Bassett%2C%20founder%20and%20head%20dog%20trainer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdogsavvyslc.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDog%20Savvy%20Positive%20Dog%20Training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20that%20even%20the%20best%20dog%20earmuffs%20won't%20be%20effective%20if%20they%20don't%20fit%20properly.%20Earmuffs%20with%20multiple%20sizes%20and%20adjustability%20ranked%20higher%2C%20as%20did%20those%20that%20accurately%20matched%20their%20advertised%20size.%20I%20also%20observed%20whether%20the%20earmuffs%20stayed%20in%20place%20while%20Olive%20ran%20across%20the%20room%20and%20jumped%20on%20and%20off%20the%20couch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransparent%20data%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20brands%20make%20big%20claims%20about%20their%20products'%20ability%20to%20block%20sound.%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20that%20such%20claims%20were%20backed%20by%20actual%20studies%20and%20data.%20I%20checked%20each%20company's%20website%20for%20information%20on%20decibel%20reduction%20and%20contacted%20brands%20directly%20if%20this%20info%20wasn't%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffective%20sound%20muffling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20To%20assess%20how%20well%20each%20earmuff%20blocked%20out%20sound%2C%20I%20conducted%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20in%20which%20I%20recorded%20Olive's%20reactions%20to%20a%20loop%20of%20dogs%20barking%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20reacts%20to%20but%20doesn't%20find%20distressing.%20First%2C%20I%20established%20her%20baseline%20response%20without%20ear%20protection%2C%20then%20I%20tested%20each%20earmuff%20while%20gradually%20increasing%20the%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20used%20for%20working%20or%20hunting%20dogs%2C%20earmuffs%20should%20withstand%20some%20rough%20treatment.%20I%20inspected%20each%20product%20for%20visible%20defects%2C%20such%20as%20loose%20stitching.%20Then%20I%20scratched%20the%20material%20with%20a%20dinner%20fork%2030-plus%20times%20and%20tugged%20on%20any%20straps%20or%20velcro%2C%20noting%20any%20sustained%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIdeally%2C%20earmuffs%20should%20be%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20as%20they%20can%20collect%20dirt%20when%20dogs%20wear%20them%20outside.%20For%20this%20test%2C%20I%20smeared%20dirt%20on%20each%20earmuff%20and%20left%20them%20overnight.%20Then%20I%20attempted%20to%20spot%20clean%20them%20and%20noted%20the%20results.%20Finally%2C%20I%20washed%20each%20earmuff%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%2C%20noting%20any%20discoloration%20or%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%20and%20return%20policy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20warranty%20offers%20peace%20of%20mind%20with%20pricier%20earmuffs%2C%20and%20a%20good%20return%20policy%20is%20important%20for%20pet%20parents%20unsure%20of%20their%20dog's%20size.%20Earmuffs%20with%20both%20received%20higher%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fhow-we-test-pet-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehow%20Business%20Insider%20Reviews%20tests%20and%20researches%20pet%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225291b9a3-f0d6-4408-84fe-8dc837432b04%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20fabric%20earmuffs%5C%22%3EBest%20fabric%20earmuffs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGrooming%20and%20noisy%20events%2C%20such%20as%20fireworks%2C%20when%20used%20alongside%20other%20strategies%20like%20training%2C%20medication%2C%20and%20environmental%20modifications%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkip%20this%20if%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20have%20a%20working%20dog%20who's%20exposed%20to%20loud%20sounds%20and%20needs%20serious%20ear%20protection%20(e.g.%2C%20hunting%20dogs%2C%20search%20and%20rescue%20dogs%2C%20and%20military%20dogs).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20snood-style%20wrap%20edged%20out%20the%20competition%20in%20one%20critical%20category%3A%20comfort.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.behaviorsolutions.guru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Leslie%20Sinn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20board-certified%20veterinary%20behaviorist%2C%20says%20that%20ear%20protection%20will%20only%20work%20if%20the%20dog%20tolerates%20wearing%20it.%20Soft%20fabric%20wraps%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126761019mrf-20%26h%3De308863fe8076ce13720d4218f8da78f031a802aa1413de73d8ae9ad27483c41%26postID%3D6a426c82778476c08ad2f971%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-earmuffs%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fhappy-hoodie-calming-cap-dogs%252Fdp%252F239670%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHappy%20Hoodie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20usually%20better%20tolerated%20by%20pets%20than%20hard-shell%20muffs%2C%20says%20trainer%20Alexandra%20Bassett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Happy%20Hoodie's%20material%20is%20soft%2C%20lightweight%2C%20and%20free%20of%20scratchy%20seams.%20Generally%2C%20Olive%20doesn't%20love%20wearing%20gear%2C%20but%20once%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20was%20in%20place%2C%20she%20didn't%20paw%20at%20it%20or%20try%20to%20remove%20it%3B%20she%20just%20continued%20resting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20area%20where%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20shines%20is%20the%20fit%2C%20which%20was%20snug%20but%20not%20too%20tight.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20comes%20in%20five%20sizes%2C%20and%20the%20stretchy%20material%20accommodates%20different%20head%20shapes.%20Olive's%20head%20circumference%20is%2014.25%20inches%2C%20so%20we%20tried%20a%20large.%20It%20stayed%20put%2C%20even%20as%20Olive%20moved%20about%20the%20room%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20seem%20too%20tight%20or%20hinder%20her%20breathing%20or%20ability%20to%20eat%20or%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20photo%20shows%20a%20dog%20wearing%20a%20purple%20fleece%20head%20wrap%2C%20looking%20alert%20in%20one%20image%20and%20resting%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed%20on%20a%20bed%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a428dd2e218c3b62535ec09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOlive%20wears%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20in%20size%20large%2C%20which%20fits%20her%20well.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Happy%20Hoodie%20may%20also%20calm%20some%20dogs%20with%20its%20gentle%20compression.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20dogs%20actually%20find%20the%20snug%2C%20swaddling%20feeling%20calming%2C%26quot%3B%20Bassett%20says.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC11639916%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20is%20limited%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20there%20is%20plenty%20of%20anecdotal%20evidence%20for%20this.%20I%20can't%20speak%20for%20every%20dog%2C%20but%20Olive%20was%20noticeably%20calmer%20on%20a%20recent%20road%20trip%20while%20wearing%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie.%20And%20during%20my%20sound-muffling%20tests%2C%20she%20was%20less%20reactive%20to%20sounds%20she%20would%20normally%20bark%20at.%20Again%2C%20I%20can't%20be%20certain%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20was%20the%20reason%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20plausible.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%2C%20every%20dog's%20experience%20will%20differ.%20Even%20though%20Olive%20didn't%20seem%20to%20mind%20wearing%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%2C%20another%20reporter%20noted%20her%20dog%20appeared%20more%20stressed%20by%20the%20snug%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20unlike%20many%20brands%20that%20exaggerate%20their%20products'%20abilities%20to%20reduce%20low-frequency%20noise%20for%20dogs%2C%20Happy%20Hoodie%20stands%20out%20for%20its%20(mostly)%20honest%20marketing%20claims.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey%20provide%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.happyhoodie.com%2Fresearch.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echart%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20testing%20results%20and%20remarks%20from%20bioacoustic%20expert%20Dr.%20Peter%20M.%20%26quot%3BSkip%26quot%3B%20Scheifele%2C%20who%20confirms%20that%20while%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20can%20help%20keep%20dogs%20calm%20during%20loud%20events%2C%20it%20can't%20block%20low-frequency%20sounds.%20This%20transparency%20is%20refreshing%20in%20a%20market%20ruled%20by%20bombastic%20claims%20that%20appeal%20to%20dog%20guardians'%20desperation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20approach%20the%20Fourth%2C%20fireworks%20have%20already%20been%20popping%20off.%20This%20has%20been%20rough%20on%20poor%20Olive%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20let%20me%20test%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20ahead%20of%20the%20bigger%20displays%20to%20come.%20%3Cstrong%3EResults%20were%20mixed.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20Olive%20still%20showed%20signs%20of%20anxiety%2C%20like%20panting%20and%20shaking%2C%20she%20settled%20down%20more%20quickly%20than%20she%20typically%20does.%20I%20can't%20base%20my%20evaluation%20on%20these%20results%20alone%2C%20though.%20Since%20these%20fireworks%20were%20unpredictable%2C%20Olive%20was%20already%20in%20a%20panicked%20state%20by%20the%20time%20I%20could%20get%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20on%20her.%20Plus%2C%20the%20fireworks%20were%20brief%20and%20not%20as%20overwhelming%20as%20the%20full%20displays%20we're%20anticipating%20on%20the%20Fourth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20open%20a%20purple%20fleece%20fabric%20tube%2C%20showing%20its%20soft%20interior%20against%20a%20light%20wood%20floor%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42952fa25092c74cca0e83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Happy%20Hoodie%20is%20soft%20and%20lightweight%2C%20providing%20comfort%20but%20lacking%20durability.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20isn't%20perfect.%20It's%20not%20the%20most%20durable%20product%2C%20and%20we%20noticed%20loose%20threads%20and%20pilling%20after%20washing.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20won't%20be%20a%20massive%20issue%20for%20most%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20give%20a%20nod%20to%20another%20tested%20band%20that%20surpassed%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20in%20our%20durability%20tests%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126761019mrf-20%26h%3D0dc981962f09923fadae1004169cba670af93b4b70f401629818bad3b1306000%26postID%3D6a426c82778476c08ad2f971%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-earmuffs%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fnanaki-calming-hoodie-ear-wraps-dogs%252Fdp%252F3617406%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENanaki%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Happy%20Hoodie%20also%20took%20a%20considerably%20long%20time%20to%20dry%2C%20whereas%20the%20Nanaki%20came%20out%20of%20the%20wash%20perfectly%20intact%20and%20dried%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231e88305-a1f4-49c5-9ae0-cac36896b9d4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20headphones%5C%22%3EBest%20headphones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dogs%20exposed%20to%20consistent%20background%20noise%2C%20like%20a%20plane%20engine%20or%20vacuum%20cleaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkip%20this%20if%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou're%20trying%20to%20block%20unpredictable%2C%20low-frequency%20sounds%20like%20fireworks%20or%20thunder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPawnix%20goes%20beyond%20the%20passive%20sound%20protection%20of%20fabric%20wraps%20and%20incorporates%20active%20noise%20cancellation%20(ANC)%20technology.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPut%20simply%2C%20ANC%20detects%20ambient%20sounds%20and%20generates%20inverted%20sound%20waves%20to%20cancel%20them%20out.%20This%20makes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpawnix.com%2Fcollections%2Fcatalog%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPawnix%3C%2Fa%3E%20useful%20in%20contexts%20where%20noise%20is%20consistent%20and%20predictable%2C%20like%20background%20machinery%20or%20the%20subway.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20technology%20won't%20be%20effective%20against%20the%20unpredictable%20booms%20of%20thunder%20or%20fireworks%20because%20electronics%20simply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126761019mrf-20%26h%3D97cb307aed318525be0a9f6a20e8e9a525f213f4521c023d5711fc8a0e68118d%26postID%3D6a426c82778476c08ad2f971%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-earmuffs%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sonos.com%252Fen%252Fblog%252Fhow-does-noise-canceling-work%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan't%20create%20sound%20waves%20fast%20enough%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20photo%20shows%20a%20gray%20padded%20dog%20ear%20cover%20with%20an%20adjustable%20chin%20strap%2C%20alongside%20a%20close-up%20of%20its%20built-in%20electronic%20module%20with%20a%20blue%20indicator%20light.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a428cfde218c3b62535ebf4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELED%20lights%20inside%20the%20ear%20panels%20show%20you%20that%20the%20noise-canceling%20components%20are%20working.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimitations%20aside%2C%20Pawnix%20performed%20best%20in%20my%20sound-muffling%20tests.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20Olive%20appeared%20to%20hear%20the%20recording%20of%20barking%20dogs%2C%20she%20didn't%20react%20%E2%80%94%20even%20at%20the%20highest%20volume.%20I%20can't%20say%20whether%20this%20was%20due%20to%20the%20earmuffs'%20sound-blocking%20foam%20or%20noise-canceling%20technology%2C%20but%20the%20results%20were%20encouraging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20also%20like%20that%20Pawnix%20uses%20Bluetooth%20to%20play%20calming%20music%20in%20your%20dog's%20ears.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BPhysics%20indicates%20that%20masking%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20management%20tool%20to%20decrease%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20scary%20sounds%20on%20our%20dogs%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feileenanddogs.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEileen%20Anderson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20writer%20who%20covers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feileenanddogs.com%2Fdogs-and-sound-welcome%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edogs%20and%20sounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20holds%20a%20master's%20in%20engineering%20with%20a%20specialty%20in%20acoustics.%20However%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consider%20that%20some%20pets%20may%20find%20the%20added%20noise%20distressing.%20After%20all%2C%20we%20can't%20ask%20our%20dogs%20how%20they%20perceive%20the%20sounds%2C%20says%20trainer%20Amanda%20Farah%2C%20and%20they%20can't%20escape%20it%20if%20it's%20too%20loud%20or%20annoying.%20Pawnix%20partially%20addresses%20this%20concern%20by%20limiting%20the%20volume%20of%20its%20speakers.%20For%20Olive%2C%20adding%20music%20was%20a%20positive%20experience.%20During%20the%20first%2010%20minutes%20of%20wearing%20these%20without%20music%2C%20she%20seemed%20tense.%20After%20playing%20music%2C%20though%2C%20she%20settled%20and%20actually%20took%20a%20nap!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20photo%20shows%20a%20dog%20wearing%20a%20gray%20padded%20ear%20cover%20with%20an%20adjustable%20chin%20strap%2C%20looking%20toward%20the%20camera%20in%20one%20image%20and%20sleeping%20on%20a%20bed%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a428cb9e218c3b62535ebeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20music%20played%20through%20the%20headphones%2C%20Olive%20settled%20in%20for%20a%20nap.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%20is%20another%20strong%20point%20for%20Pawnix%2C%20with%20five%20standard%20sizes%20and%20the%20option%20to%20order%20custom%20sizes%20for%20dogs%20with%20unique%20proportions.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pawnix%20also%20features%20drawstrings%20that%20tighten%20around%20the%20neck.%20Olive%20fell%20at%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20medium%20size%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20little%20too%20big%20for%20her.%20If%20you%20find%20the%20Pawnix%20flops%20around%20on%20your%20dog's%20head%2C%20the%20brand%20recommends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpawnix.com%2Fpages%2Fwelcome%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadjusting%20the%20electronic%20components%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20tighten%20the%20elastic%20bands.%20They%20also%20offer%20free%20exchanges%20if%20you're%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20area%20(and%20not%20an%20insignificant%20one)%20where%20Pawnix%20falls%20short%20is%20its%20lack%20of%20transparency%20regarding%20its%20noise-reducing%20capabilities.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unlike%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie%20or%20the%20Rex%20Specs%20(another%20earmuff%20I%20tested)%2C%20there%20are%20no%20studies%20or%20concrete%20evidence%20to%20support%20claims%20of%20a%2030%20dB%20reduction%20in%20sound.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20company%20about%20this%2C%20but%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22faf7df17-46b2-4c6e-93d9-45018c4cde8d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20else%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EWhat%20else%20we%20tested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20photo%20shows%20a%20dog%20sleeping%20while%20wearing%20two%20different%20ear%20wraps%3A%20a%20dark%20gray%20fabric%20headband%20in%20one%20image%20and%20a%20tan%20protective%20hood%20in%20the%20other.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a429a4da25092c74cca0ecb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20also%20tested%20the%20Nanaki%20calming%20band%20and%20the%20Rex%20Specs%20earmuffs.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126761019mrf-20%26h%3D0dc981962f09923fadae1004169cba670af93b4b70f401629818bad3b1306000%26postID%3D6a426c82778476c08ad2f971%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-earmuffs%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fnanaki-calming-hoodie-ear-wraps-dogs%252Fdp%252F3617406%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENanaki%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(%2419-%2422%20at%20Chewy)%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20has%20a%20design%20similar%20to%20the%20Happy%20Hoodie.%20It's%20a%20stretchy%20band%20of%20fabric%20that%20slides%20over%20your%20dog's%20head%20to%20provide%20a%20barrier%20against%20sound.%20The%20material%20is%20buttery%20soft%2C%20and%20it%20hugged%20Olive's%20head%20without%20choking%20her.%20However%2C%20Nanaki%20didn't%20beat%20Happy%20Hoodie%20for%20the%20same%20reason%20I%20found%20fault%20with%20Pawnix%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20lack%20of%20testing%20or%20data%20to%20support%20claims%20of%20%26quot%3Beffective%20noise%20reduction.%26quot%3B%20I'd%20prefer%20to%20see%20some%20kind%20of%20concrete%20evidence%20that%20this%20works.%20Nanaki%20also%20performed%20slightly%20worse%20than%20Happy%20Hoodie%20in%20my%20sound-blocking%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126761019mrf-20%26h%3D3dfce099fd9c655def63d392314fd1f0b5cee1636037fc9cba87a9c39a5cab37%26postID%3D6a426c82778476c08ad2f971%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-earmuffs%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Frex-specs-dog-ear-pro%252Fdp%252F3273574%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERex%20Specs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%2474%20at%20Chewy)%3A%20These%20stretchy%20earmuffs%20were%20designed%20to%20protect%20military%20dogs'%20hearing%20and%20feature%20sound-absorbing%20foam%20inserts.%20They're%20well-made%20and%20durable.%20Rex%20Specs%20are%20also%20tested%20for%20sound%20reduction%20in%20accordance%20with%20guidelines%20recommended%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fdocs%2F98-126%2Fpdfs%2FCriteriaDoc_98-126.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20for%20Occupational%20Safety%20and%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NIOSH).%20Results%20are%20displayed%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rexspecs.com%2Fblogs%2Fnews%2Fcanine-hearing-threshold-shifts-due-to-noise-exposure-specifically-transportation-noise-and-general-outline-of-the-audiological-and-acoustical-testing-of-rex-specs-ear-pro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20showing%20that%20Rex%20Specs%20reduced%20noise%20exposure%20by%2018%20and%2024%20dB%20at%20very%20low%20frequencies%20(20%20Hz%20to%20120%20Hz).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Rex%20Specs%20fell%20short%20in%20the%20area%20my%20experts%20consider%20most%20important%3A%20comfort.%20These%20felt%20too%20tight%20around%20Olive's%20throat%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20complaint%20in%20customer%20reviews.%20Olive%20appeared%20notably%20distressed%20wearing%20these.%20I%20also%20found%20them%20to%20be%20fairly%20ineffective%20in%20my%20soundproofing%20tests%2C%20which%20was%20disappointing%20given%20their%20high%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232af5671-5c26-48a9-9858-4e93615db524%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20dog%20earmuffs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20sound-blocking%20products%20available%20for%20dogs%2C%20but%20many%20aren't%20worth%20buying.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20best%20dog%20earmuffs%20are%20the%20ones%20your%20pet%20is%20comfortable%20wearing%20and%20that%20seem%20to%20calm%20them.%20Here's%20what%20my%20experts%20recommend%20focusing%20on%20when%20choosing%20ear%20protection%20for%20your%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfortable%20materials%20and%20design%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20underestimate%20how%20important%20comfort%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Bassett%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20dog%20spends%20the%20entire%20time%20pawing%20at%20it%20or%20trying%20to%20remove%20it%2C%20it's%20probably%20not%20helping%20much%20emotionally.%26quot%3B%20Look%20for%20lightweight%2C%20soft%20materials%20that%20your%20dog%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20accept%20wearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccurate%20fit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Don't%20skip%20the%20measuring%20tape!%20Bassett%20says%20getting%20an%20accurate%20fit%20is%20important%20for%20two%20reasons%3A%20it%20helps%20keep%20sound%20out%20and%20makes%20the%20dog%20more%20comfortable.%20The%20fabric%20wraps%20featured%20here%20aren't%20adjustable%2C%20but%20they%20come%20in%20multiple%20sizes%20and%20can%20stretch%20to%20accommodate%20bigger%20heads.%20The%20Pawnix%20can%20be%20tightened%20around%20the%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20related%20to%20efficacy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20hard-shell%20earmuffs%2C%20Bassett%20says%20she%20likes%20to%20see%20companies%20provide%20actual%20decibel-reduction%20data%20rather%20than%20just%20marketing%20language.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20for%20working%20dogs%20whose%20hearing%20may%20be%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranties%20and%20good%20return%20policies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20earmuffs%2C%20like%20the%20Pawnix%20and%20Rex%20Specs%2C%20are%20pricey%20items.%20And%2C%20as%20I%20learned%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20get%20the%20right%20size%20on%20the%20first%20try.%20A%20solid%20warranty%20and%20return%20policy%20protect%20your%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bd6c288-7e42-4a3a-88b9-ad18448cbc54%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20acclimate%20a%20dog%20to%20wearing%20ear%20protection%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20acclimate%20a%20dog%20to%20wearing%20ear%20protection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20gradually%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ideally%2C%20long%20before%20you%20actually%20need%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bassett%20says.%20She%20recommends%20planning%20for%20four%20to%20six%20weeks%20of%20gradual%20conditioning.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20people%20make%20is%20pulling%20out%20ear%20muffs%20for%20the%20first%20time%20during%20fireworks%20and%20trying%20to%20put%20them%20on%20an%20already%20panicking%20dog.%20That%20usually%20backfires.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBassett%20lays%20out%20the%20following%20steps%20for%20introducing%20dog%20ear%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3ELet%20the%20dog%20investigate%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPair%20it%20with%20high-value%20treats%20like%20string%20cheese%2C%20cooked%20meat%2C%20or%20lunch%20meat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBriefly%20touch%20around%20the%20ears%20before%20putting%20the%20gear%20on.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPut%20it%20on%20for%20just%20a%20second%20or%20two%20at%20first%2C%20and%20remove%20quickly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReward%20heavily%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20you%20take%20the%20gear%20off.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESlowly%20build%20duration%20over%20multiple%20sessions%20over%20the%20course%20of%20about%20four%20to%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227228898f-cd7d-49d0-b529-8e6bc86b8f05%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDog%20earmuffs%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20other%20strategies%20can%20pet%20owners%20use%20to%20calm%20their%20noise-averse%20dog%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Farah%20suggests%20seeing%20a%20veterinarian%20to%20rule%20out%20pain%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20contributing%20factor.%20Once%20medical%20conditions%20are%20ruled%20out%2C%20you%20can%20take%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftodaysveterinarypractice.com%2Fbehavior%2Fnoise-storm-phobias-anxiety-in-dogs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultimodal%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20might%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesensitization%20and%20counterconditioning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20techniques%20involve%20exposing%20your%20dog%20to%20the%20scary%20sound%20at%20a%20low%20volume%20while%20offering%20treats.%20Gradually%20increase%20the%20volume%2C%20always%20staying%20below%20your%20dog's%20stress%20threshold.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExercise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20can%20predict%20the%20noisy%20event%2C%20plan%20to%20tire%20your%20dog%20out%20beforehand%20and%20get%20potty%20breaks%20out%20of%20the%20way%20so%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20outside.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesignate%20a%20safe%20place%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20could%20be%20a%20bathroom%2C%20basement%2C%20or%20closet%20filled%20with%20blankets%2C%20favorite%20toys%2C%20and%20chews%20for%20distraction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoundproof%20your%20home%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EClose%20windows%20and%20doors%2C%20and%20draw%20curtains%20to%20reduce%20noise%20levels.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlay%20background%20noise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Turn%20on%20the%20TV%2C%20play%20white%20noise%2C%20or%20put%20on%20soothing%20classical%20music%20to%20muffle%20scary%20sounds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffer%20enrichment%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEngage%20your%20dog%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-pu