mpUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amanda%20Batula%20Leaving%20%E2%80%98Summer%20House%E2%80%99%20After%2010%20Seasons%20in%20Wake%20of%20%23Scamanda%20Controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782756467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236784481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20other%20shoe%20has%20dropped%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CSummer%20House%E2%80%9D%20scandal%3A%20Amanda%20Batula%20will%20not%20be%20returning%20for%20Season%2011%20of%20the%20Bravo%20show%2C%20Variety%20has%20learned.%20Though%20this%20development%20may%20be%20obvious%20%E2%80%94%20in%20that%20Batula%20upended%20her%20life%20and%20career%20by%20beginning%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%20castmate%20West%20Wilson%2C%20who%E2%80%99s%20also%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Kate%20Aurthur%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Newsom%20and%20Anthropic%20reach%20deal%20to%20give%20local%20governments%20discounted%20access%20to%20Claude%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WASHINGTON%20DC%2C%20UNITED%20STATES%20-%20MAY%2020%3A%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20(D-CA)%20speaks%20to%20reporters%20inside%20the%20U.S.%20Capitol%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20on%20May%2020%2C%202026.%20(Photo%20by%20Nathan%20Posner%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42b162360acd489560d0de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGovernor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20speaks%20to%20reporters%20inside%20the%20U.S.%20Capitol%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20on%20May%2020%2C%202026.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Posner%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGavin%20Newsom%20reached%20a%20deal%20with%20Anthropic%20to%20expand%20the%20use%20of%20Claude%20products%20across%20California's%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20agreement%20would%20make%20Claude%20the%20first%20AI%20tool%20available%20to%20all%20state%20agencies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20terms%20include%20free%20workforce%20training%20and%20technical%20support%20from%20Anthropic%20staff.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESAN%20FRANCISCO%20%E2%80%94%20Gov.%20Gavin%20Newsom%20has%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20Anthropic%20to%20expand%20the%20use%20of%20Claude%20products%20across%20California's%20government%20at%20a%20discounted%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%2C%20first%20shared%20with%20POLITICO%2C%20would%20make%20Claude%20the%20first%20artificial%20intelligence%20tool%20available%20to%20all%20state%20agencies%20and%20local%20governments.%20It%20comes%20amid%20a%20monthslong%20fight%20between%20Anthropic%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20which%20has%20restricted%20the%20rollout%20of%20the%20company's%20most%20advanced%20models%20and%20designated%20it%20a%20risk%20to%20the%20national%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsom's%20deal%20seeks%20to%20drive%20broader%20adoption%20of%20Claude%20by%20cutting%20the%20AI%20chatbot's%20price%20in%20half%20for%20state%20government%20agencies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Californian%20cities%20and%20counties%20that%20decide%20to%20take%20advantage.%20The%20terms%20also%20include%20free%20workforce%20training%20and%20technical%20support%20from%20Anthropic%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20departments%20are%20going%20to%20switch%20their%20usage%20to%20this%20contract%2C%20and%20that's%20very%20much%20our%20intent%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Given%2C%20California's%20chief%20information%20officer%20and%20director%20of%20the%20state%20Department%20of%20Technology%2C%20told%20POLITICO.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20see%20that%20folks%20are%20going%20to%20be%20using%20a%20tool%20more%2C%20we%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%2C%20as%20the%20state%2C%20have%20negotiated%20the%20best%20possible%20price%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20%F0%9F%A4%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAnthropicAI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AnthropicAI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe're%20entering%20a%20partnership%20to%20strengthen%20cybersecurity%20and%20provide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fclaudeai%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ClaudeAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20state%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20California%20local%20governments%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%2050%25%20discount.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Golden%20State%20helped%20build%20Silicon%20Valley%20%E2%80%94%20and%20every%20Californian%20should%20benefit%20from%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20(%40CAgovernor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FCAgovernor%2Fstatus%2F2071598083717382261%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2029%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20March%2C%20Newsom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.ca.gov%2F2026%2F03%2F30%2Fas-trump-rolls-back-protections-governor-newsom-signs-first-of-its-kind-executive-order-to-strengthen-ai-protections-and-responsible-use%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%20an%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20to%20raise%20standards%20for%20AI%20companies%20seeking%20state%20contracts%20and%20allow%20California%20to%20separate%20its%20procurement%20process%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20order%20could%20directly%20challenge%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20Newsom's%20administration%20says%20the%20new%20Anthropic%20deal%20was%20not%20intended%20as%20a%20rebuke%20or%20response%20to%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsom%20has%20issued%20a%20series%20of%20executive%20orders%20to%20promote%20generative%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20improve%20government%20efficiency.%20Claude%20is%20already%20used%20for%20certain%20state%20tasks%2C%20from%20patching%20code%20to%20supporting%20a%20platform%20that%20collects%20input%20on%20the%20public's%20feelings%20about%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20a%20likely%20presidential%20run%2C%20the%20governor%20has%20tried%20to%20position%20himself%20as%20both%20an%20ally%20to%20the%20booming%2C%20yet%20increasingly%20controversial%20AI%20industry%20and%20an%20advocate%20for%20protecting%20Americans%20from%20the%20disruption%20it%20could%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Newsom%20has%20turned%20his%20attention%20to%20the%20potential%20widespread%20job%20losses%20AI%20could%20trigger.%20He%20issued%20another%20executive%20order%20last%20month%2C%20tapping%20state%20agencies%20to%20explore%20policies%20that%20could%20help%20California%20respond%20faster%20to%20AI-driven%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2026%2F05%2F22%2Flabor-leaders-see-newsoms-ai-workforce-eo-as-softer-than-advertised-00933385%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrew%20mixed%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20frustration%20from%20labor%20leaders%20who%20have%20warned%20Newsom%20that%20they%20will%20not%20support%20a%20future%20presidential%20bid%20unless%20he%20enacts%20stronger%20worker%20protections%20against%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Newsom%20launched%20a%20new%20tool%20to%20track%20AI-related%20job%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20should%20not%20replace%20the%20human%20work%20of%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Newsom%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20regarding%20his%20Anthropic%20deal.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20help%20our%20workers%20move%20faster%2C%20solve%20problems%20more%20effectively%2C%20and%20deliver%20better%20results%20for%20Californians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20administration%20has%20put%20Anthropic%20products%20to%20work%20across%20a%20range%20of%20government%20services.%20Its%20models%20helped%20develop%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flinks.us1.defend.egress.com%2FWarning%3FcrId%3D6a3f0881696a69796d165788%26Domain%3Dpolitico.com%26Threat%3DeNpzrShJLcpLzAEADmkDRA%253D%253D%26Lang%3Den%26%40OriginalLink%3Dwww.gov.ca.gov%26Base64Url%3DeNolzVEOAjEIBNATsbhN9MPbYCWWpEsbwK3e3jZ-Td58zJSI7nfEMcb2aueWaQWmS7rinnC_4SSbNgPl4e2ASm_NhX0ZRCWEQs7paNDJQtlgSBQIzgV6q5K_wJ_OFg6kT6CcubJRMBh7b-ryqAwkcw08Vv__PFgDf2ISO6Y%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrently%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state's%20digital%20assistant%2C%20Poppy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20gateways%20for%20state%20employees%20to%20start%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude%20underpins%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.ca.gov%2F2026%2F05%2F07%2Fgovernor-newsom-launches-engaged-california-statewide-for-the-first-time-to-give-all-californians-a-stronger-voice-in-ai-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20engagement%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Newsom%20has%20employed%20most%20recently%20for%20gathering%20residents'%20views%20on%20how%20AI%20is%20impacting%20their%20jobs%20and%20the%20future%20of%20work.%20It's%20also%20a%20tool%20for%20customer%20service%20at%20the%20California%20DMV%20and%20for%20internal%20workflows%20that%20assist%20Medicaid%20recipients%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20Care%20Services.%20And%20the%20state%20Department%20of%20Technology%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtech.com%2Fsecurity%2Fcalifornia-texas-among-first-states-in-anthropic-cyber-cohort%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20cybersecurity%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Anthropic%2C%20using%20Claude%20to%20spot%20vulnerabilities%20in%20state%20code%20and%20critical%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20said%20the%20state%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20secure%20similar%20discount%20deals%20with%20other%20AI%20companies%20and%20tech%20providers.%20It%20invited%20AI%20model%20providers%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20state%20back%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia's%20first%20meeting%20with%20Anthropic%20for%20the%20deal%20was%20March%205%2C%20the%20same%20day%20the%20Pentagon%20formally%20labeled%20the%20Claude%20maker%20a%20supply%20chain%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsom's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.ca.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2026%2F03%2F3.30-FINAL-Trusted-AI-Procurement-EO-N-5-26.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarch%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20came%20after%20the%20Pentagon's%20decision%2C%20directed%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Technology%20to%20review%20any%20such%20federal%20designations.%20If%20it%20found%20the%20designation%20to%20be%20improper%2C%20the%20order%20instructed%20state%20officials%20to%20issue%20guidance%20allowing%20California%20to%20continue%20doing%20business%20with%20that%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20supply%20chain%20risk%20designation%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20an%20issue%20that%20we%20faced%20while%20signing%20and%20negotiating%20this%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20Given%20said%2C%20declining%20to%20elaborate%20on%20the%20reason.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20didn't%20come%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20department%20is%20formalizing%20recommendations%20for%20Newsom%20on%20that%20part%20of%20the%20order%20and%20expects%20those%20to%20be%20ready%20by%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20originally%20%3C%2Fem%3Eappeared%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2026%2F06%2F29%2Fexclusive-newsom-anthropic-ink-deal-to-expand-government-use-00979584%3FICID%3Dref_fark%26utm_campaign%3Dfark%26utm_content%3Dlink%26utm_medium%3Dwebsite%26utm_source%3Dfark%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eon%20POLITICO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2026%2F06%2F29%2Fexclusive-newsom-anthropic-ink-deal-to-expand-government-use-00979584%3FICID%3Dref_fark%26utm_campaign%3Dfark%26utm_content%3Dlink%26utm_medium%3Dwebsite%26utm_source%3Dfark%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eand%20is%20courtesy%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20which%20harnesses%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20company's%20newsrooms%20to%20publish%20ambitious%20scoops%2C%20investigations%2C%20interviews%2C%20opinion%20pieces%2C%20and%20analysis.%20It%20allows%20journalists%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20from%20POLITICO%2C%20Business%20Insider%2C%20WELT%2C%20BILD%2C%20Onet%2C%20and%20Fakt%20%E2%80%94%20to%20collaborate%20on%20major%20stories%20for%20an%20international%20audience%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20across%20platforms.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewsom-anthropic-ink-deal-expand-government-use-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782756444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42b17a360acd489560d0df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewsom-anthropic-ink-deal-expand-government-use-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20agreement%20would%20make%20Claude%20the%20first%20artificial%20intelligence%20tool%20available%20to%20all%20state%20agencies%20and%20local%20governments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Probability%20of%20Miracles%E2%80%99%20Amazon%20TV%20Series%20Casts%20Brian%20Tee%2C%20Ben%20Feldman%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782756000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236798444%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video%20TV%20adaptation%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Probability%20of%20Miracles%E2%80%9D%20has%20added%20two%20new%20cast%20members.%20Variety%20has%20learned%20exclusively%20that%20Brian%20Tee%20and%20Ben%20Feldman%20are%20both%20set%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20series%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Wendy%20Wunder%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name.%20Production%20on%20the%20series%20is%20now%20underway%20in%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Joseph%20Otterson%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20student-loan%20overhaul%20takes%20effect%20July%201%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20deadline%20for%20borrowers%20to%20act%20on%20repayment%20changes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224936%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22College%20graduation%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42894da25092c74cca0dcf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222586%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20student-loan%20repayment%20overhaul%20takes%20effect%20on%20July%201.%3Cp%3Ehxdbzxy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20sweeping%20student-loan%20changes%20take%20effect%20July%201.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESAVE%20borrowers%20aren't%20required%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan%20right%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey'll%20receive%20a%2090-day%20timeframe%20in%20which%20they%20can%20select%20a%20new%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%2C%20July%201%20is%20the%20starting%20point%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20deadline%20%E2%80%94%20to%20act%20on%20repayment%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20eliminated%20the%20SAVE%20repayment%20plan%20in%20March%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20recommended%20that%20the%207%20million%20enrolled%20borrowers%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20plan%20and%20begin%20making%20payments%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20However%2C%20switching%20before%20July%201%20is%20not%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeginning%20July%201%2C%20the%20department%20said%20it%20would%20start%20sending%20emails%20to%20SAVE%20borrowers%20about%20their%20timeline%20for%20switching%20plans.%20Upon%20receiving%20this%20email%2C%20which%20may%20come%20later%20than%20July%201%2C%20borrowers%20will%20have%2090%20days%20to%20select%20a%20new%20plan.%20If%20they%20do%20not%20select%20a%20new%20plan%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%2090-day%20period%2C%20they%20will%20automatically%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20standard%20repayment%20plan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-most-expensive-repayment-trump-changes-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20expensive%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20notice%20the%20department%20recently%20sent%20to%20SAVE%20borrowers%2C%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20borrowers%20have%20already%20switched%20plans.%20In%20a%20recent%20court%20filing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-have-more-time-repayment-trump-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20department%20affirmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20because%20borrowers%20will%20be%20transitioned%20in%20waves%2C%20some%20%26quot%3Bwill%20get%20even%20more%20time%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20earliest%20possible%20transition%20deadline%20of%20September%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20student-loan%20repayment%20overhaul%20will%20bring%20a%20host%20of%20changes%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20SAVE%20transition.%20Also%20beginning%20July%201%2C%20new%20repayment%20plans%20and%20borrowing%20caps%20will%20take%20effect%2C%20and%20borrowers%20expect%20to%20see%20their%20monthly%20bills%20increase%20%E2%80%94%20some%20by%20hundreds%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOngoing%20litigation%20could%20halt%20some%20of%20those%20changes.%20A%20lawsuit%20filed%20in%20March%20aims%20to%20stop%20the%20forced%20transition%20of%20borrowers%20off%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20and%20a%20federal%20judge%20recently%20blocked%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcourt-blocks-student-loan-borrowing-caps-nurses-trump-repayment-overhaul-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edepartment's%20narrowed%20definition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20professional%20degree%20from%20taking%20effect%20July%201%2C%20which%20would%20have%20placed%20lower%20borrowing%20limits%20on%20some%20advanced%20degree%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20previously%20said%20that%20these%20changes%20are%20intended%20to%20simplify%20a%20complex%20repayment%20system%20and%20curb%20excessive%20borrowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20student%20loans%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeATa4iQeOzHtXhvcsvVIBfQLs3uacbq2N6OSrC5Eti5s6i1A%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Efill%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-overhaul-borrowers-dont-need-to-act-trump-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782755966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a428958e218c3b62535eba8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-overhaul-borrowers-dont-need-to-act-trump-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20student-loan%20changes%20take%20effect%20on%20July%201%2C%20but%20the%20millions%20of%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20wi