BANDYOPADHYAY%20AND%20KAUSHIK%20PRADHAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20reasons%20UBS%20sees%20gold%20surging%2030%25%20in%20the%20next%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gold%20bar%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a427fd7360acd489560ceb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUBS%20forecasts%20gold%20prices%20to%20rise%2028%25%20to%20%245%2C200%20per%20ounce%20in%20the%20next%2012%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bank%20cites%20Fed%20policy%20shifts%2C%20a%20weaker%20dollar%2C%20and%20central%20bank%20buying%20as%20key%20drivers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUBS%20suggests%20a%20mid-single%20digit%20gold%20allocation%20for%20diversification%20amid%20market%20and%20economic%20stress.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-silver-price-today-market-crash-outlook-forecast-warsh-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erough%20patch%20for%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20UBS%20says%20the%20precious%20metal%20is%20set%20to%20surge%20about%2028%25%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20prices%20are%20down%2023%25%20since%20their%20January%20highs%20to%20around%20%244%2C040%20an%20ounce%2C%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-silver-copper-commodities-fed-rate-cuts-metals-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E150%25%20gain%20from%20early%202024%20to%20early%202026%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20June%2025%20note%2C%20UBS%20said%20a%20mix%20of%20three%20factors%20should%20drive%20a%20recovery%20in%20prices%20to%20about%20%245%2C200%20an%20ounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20the%20bank%20said%20that%20investors%20are%20overestimating%20the%20hawkishness%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20after%20Kevin%20Warsh's%20first%20meeting%20as%20the%20central%20bank's%20chairman.%20The%20Fed's%20next%20move%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20cut%20than%20a%20hike%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20and%20when%20those%20expectations%20shift%2C%20it%20should%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20gold.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20tends%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates%20when%20the%20economy%20needs%20a%20boost%2C%20which%20is%20also%20when%20investors%20might%20seek%20out%20safe%20haven%20assets%20like%20gold.%20UBS%20said%20they%20expect%20economic%20growth%20in%20slow%20over%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20the%20US%20dollar%20should%20weaken%20as%20long%20positioning%20in%20the%20currency%20is%20%26quot%3Bstretched%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20as%20fiscal%20deficits%20continue%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20weaker%20dollar%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20powerful%20tailwind%20for%20gold%2C%26quot%3B%20Ulrike%20Hoffmann-Burchardi%2C%20the%20bank's%20global%20head%20of%20equities%2C%20said%20in%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20third%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20global%20central%20banks%20should%20continue%20buying%20up%20the%20yellow%20metal.%20In%20May%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Poland%20and%20China%20bought%2018%20and%2010%20metric%20tons%20of%20gold%2C%20respectively.%20The%20bank%20said%20annual%20demand%20should%20remain%20steady%2C%20providing%20a%20floor%20for%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20how%20gold%20fits%20into%20a%20portfolio%2C%20Hoffmann-Burchardi%20said%20UBS%20an%20appropriate%20allocation%20for%20investors%20might%20be%20in%20the%20mid-single%20digit%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffmann-Burchardi%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIts%20relatively%20low%20historical%20correlation%20with%20traditional%20asset%20classes%20means%20that%20it%20should%20add%20to%20overall%20portfolio%20resilience%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bullish%20UBS%20outlook%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-forecast-outlook-etf-interest-rates-sell-off-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eother%20banks%20have%20slashed%20their%202026%20price%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20now%20sees%20the%20rising%20less%20than%20it%20previously%20predicted%2C%20hitting%20%244%2C900%20an%20ounce%20by%20year-end%2C%20down%20from%20%245%2C400.%20ING%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20expects%20gold%20to%20end%20the%20year%20around%20%244%2C600%2C%20lower%20than%20its%20earlier%20forecast%20of%20%245%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-prices-prediction-rally-fed-weak-dollar-fed-interest-rates-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782752463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a428827a25092c74cca0dc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-prices-prediction-rally-fed-weak-dollar-fed-interest-rates-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20rough%20patch%20for%20gold%20prices%2C%20UBS%20says%20the%20precious%20metal%20is%20set%20to%20surge%20about%2028%25%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months%2C%20boosted%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20tailwinds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Academy%20Taps%20%E2%80%98Memento%E2%80%99%20Producer%20Jennifer%20Todd%20for%20Governors%20Awards%2C%20Succeeding%20Jennifer%20Fox%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782752460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236798597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Academy%20Producers%20Branch%20governor%20Jennifer%20Todd%20will%20produce%20the%2017th%20Governors%20Awards%2C%20marking%20her%20first%20time%20leading%20the%20event.%20She%20takes%20over%20duties%20for%20Jennifer%20Fox%2C%20who%20had%20produced%20the%20event%20for%20seven%20years.%20Honorary%20Oscars%20will%20be%20presented%20to%20actor%20Glenn%20Close%2C%20director%20Ridley%20Scott%20and%20animator%20Floyd%20Norman.%20Producers%20Christine%20Vachon%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Clayton%20Davis%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20the%20Cosori%20TurboBlaze%20is%20the%20best%20air%20fryer%20we%20tested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20cosori%20air%20fryer%20and%20brussel%20sprouts%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a398e2db9227396386dc91c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20testing%20many%20air%20fryers%2C%20the%20Cosori%20TurboBlaze%20was%20our%20best%20overall%20pick%20for%20its%20consistent%20performance%2C%20sleek%20design%2C%20and%20affordable%20price.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20so%20many%20air%20fryers%20on%20the%20market%2C%20and%20most%20of%20them%20are%20basket-style%20models%2C%20so%20how%20do%20you%20choose%20the%20right%20one%3F%20Lucky%20for%20you%2C%20dear%20reader.%20I%20have%20tested%20so%20many%20of%20them%20and%20can%20match%20the%20perfect%20air%20fryer%20to%20the%20user%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20you%20are%20looking%20for.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dffcabbbe2c84e501efc0781e15b367130bad65cd5fd7ba3e88fdd5c243650624%26postID%3D6a398b8a24f8ed9bcbf605b7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fcosori-turboblaze-air-fryer-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0C33CHG99%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosori%20TurboBlaze%3C%2Fa%3E%20air%20fryer%20is%20the%20one%20I%20can%20recommend%20to%20most%20people%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20won%20the%20coveted%20Best%20Overall%20spot%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-air-fryers-reviewed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20air%20fryer%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20testing%2C%20it%20was%20our%20best%20overall%20air%20fryer%20because%20it%20performed%20consistently%20across%20everything%20I%20cooked%20and%20was%20a%20great%20value.%20It%20normally%20retails%20for%20%24120%2C%20but%20is%20often%20on%20sale%2C%20like%20right%20now%2C%20for%20%2490.%20At%20that%20price%2C%20it%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20since%20the%20machine%20is%20incredibly%20powerful%20and%20sleek.%20It%20was%20the%20air%20fryer%20I%20kept%20in%20my%20kitchen%20after%20testing%20was%20complete%20because%20it%20gave%20me%20the%20best%20results%20and%20had%20the%20capacity%20right%20for%20my%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2b33313-a329-49e2-a6f6-35a431712167%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Why%20it's%20the%20best%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Cosori%20TurboBlaze%20is%20the%20best%20air%20fryer%20we%20tested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cosori%20air%20fryer%20on%20a%20counter%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe5ba4c9dd4cb81cda8ca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20perfect%20air%20fryer%20may%20not%20exist%2C%20but%20this%20is%20about%20as%20close%20as%20I%20have%20come%20for%20its%20price%20point%20and%20ability%20to%20please%20most%20households.%20It%20has%20a%20six-quart%20capacity%2C%20and%20its%20performance%20excelled%20in%20all%20tests.%20It%20crisped%20the%20edges%20of%20our%20Brussels%20sprouts%20and%20made%20fresh%20chicken%20wings%20that%20rivaled%20any%20wing%20shop.%20It%20was%20also%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20as%20you%20just%20need%20to%20pop%20the%20basket%20into%20the%20dishwasher.%20At%20a%20price%20point%20around%20%24100%2C%20it's%20a%20steal%20and%20made%20to%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a254aea-464e-4096-a101-aca22c8f2347%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cooking%20performance%5C%22%3EIt%20nailed%20the%20foods%20people%20actually%20make%20in%20an%20air%20fryer.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22brussel%20sprouts%20in%20a%20cosori%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe5ba4ba7ef34b41f36a2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20Brussels%20sprouts%20outer%20leaves%20are%20crisp%20and%20slightly%20charred%2C%20while%20the%20center%20remains%20tender%20and%20not%20dried%20out.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TurboBlaze%20turned%20in%20some%20of%20the%20strongest%20cooking%20results%20among%20the%20models%20I%20tested.%20Frozen%20fries%20came%20out%20evenly%20browned%20with%20crispy%20exteriors%20and%20fluffy%20interiors%2C%20and%20they%20finished%20very%20close%20to%20the%20timing%20listed%20on%20most%20packages.%20That%20accuracy%20may%20sound%20minor%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20consistent%20across%20the%20models%20we%20tested%2C%20as%20some%20required%20much%20more%20time%20during%20certain%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChicken%20wings%20were%20another%20standout%20for%20the%20TurboBlaze.%20They%20achieved%20a%20deeply%20brown%20skin%20with%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20crispness%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20intervene%20much.%20The%20basket's%20capacity%20also%20allowed%20me%20to%20make%20a%20generous%20first%20batch%2C%20which%20was%20rare%20with%20single-basket%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVegetables%20such%20as%20Brussels%20sprouts%20also%20performed%20exceptionally%20well.%20The%20outer%20leaves%20are%20crisp%20and%20slightly%20charred%2C%20while%20the%20center%20remains%20tender%20and%20not%20dried%20out.%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20noticeable%20hot%20spots%20or%20undercooked%20areas%20when%20I%20tested%20this%20air%20fryer%2C%20which%20also%20showed%20me%20that%20it%20is%20incredibly%20consistent.%20It%20delivered%20predictable%20results%2C%20and%20it%20made%20it%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5b77c2d-b095-4ee3-b086-74ea3c4e931b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ease%20of%20Use%5C%22%3EThe%20six-quart%20basket%20is%20the%20right%20size%20for%20everyday%20cooking.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22veggies%20cooked%20incosori%20tuboblaze%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a39902936d7e6f260b7814b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%206-quart%20capacity%20is%20great%20for%20families%20and%20meal%20prepping.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%206-quart%20capacity%20hits%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20most%20households.%20It's%20large%20enough%20to%20cook%20a%20full%20batch%20of%20wings%2C%20a%20generous%20serving%20of%20vegetables%2C%20or%20enough%20fries%20for%20a%20family%20of%20four%20without%20taking%20up%20too%20much%20real%20estate.%20The%20basket%20easily%20slides%20in%20and%20out%20and%20feels%20balanced%20when%20carrying%20heavier%20foods.%20Well%2C%20larger%20dual-basket%20machines%20offer%20much%20more%20flexibility%20in%20what%20you%20can%20cook%20and%20how%20much%20you%20can%20cook%2C%20but%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20significantly%20heavier%20and%20take%20up%20much%20more%20counter%20space.%20The%20TurboBlaze%20is%20a%20single-basket%20design%20that%20keeps%20it%20simple%20while%20still%20providing%20enough%20capacity%20for%20everyday%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca1f389b-0ffc-4a28-8bc4-550d76e07d74%5C%22%3EThe%20controls%20are%20simple%20enough%20for%20distracted%20weeknights.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20adjusts%20controls%20of%20the%20cosori%20tuboblaze%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a399080b9227396386dc944%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20display%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20see.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20touch%20screen%20interface%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20parts%20of%20the%20machine.%20It%20has%20a%20large%20number%20of%20clearly%20labeled%20functions%20and%20responsive%20controls%20that%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20adjust%20the%20settings%20quickly%2C%20even%20mid-cook.%20The%20display%20is%20bright%20enough%20to%20read%20at%20a%20glance%2C%20but%20remains%20clean%20and%20uncluttered%20when%20the%20machine%20is%20off.%20It%20looks%20super%20sleek.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20the%20built-in%20Shake%20reminder%2C%20which%20is%20genuinely%20useful%20rather%20than%20annoying%20because%20I%20get%20distracted%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20There%20are%20presets%20for%20air%20frying%2C%20roasting%2C%20baking%2C%20broiling%2C%20reheating%2C%20dehydrating%2C%20proofing%2C%20frozen%20foods%2C%20and%20keeping%20food%20warm%2C%20which%20are%20convenient%20without%20making%20the%20interface%20feel%20overwhelming.%20Overall%2C%20this%20machine%20simplifies%20cooking%20rather%20than%20adding%20another%20layer%20of%20complexity%20to%20your%20weeknight%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216d86869-8445-4009-95ce-23b4f8daae09%5C%22%3EIt%20looks%20better%20than%20most%20air%20fryers.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cosori%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a39941836d7e6f260b78183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sleek%20design%20looks%20nice%20in%20my%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20air%20fryers%20perform%20well%20but%20look%20like%20oversized%20plastic%20boxes.%20The%20TurboBlaze%20stands%20out%20because%20it%20feels%20thoughtfully%20designed%20and%20suitable%20for%20any%20home%20style.%20It%20has%20a%20sleek%20exterior%2C%20a%20flush%20touchscreen%20that%20disappears%20when%20it's%20off%2C%20and%20is%20relatively%20compact%20for%20a%20six-quart%20basket.%20We%20often%20leave%20it%20on%20the%20counter%20full-time%20during%20busy%20weeks%2C%20and%2C%20at%20a%20minimum%2C%20it%20doesn't%20bother%20me%2C%20even%20though%20I%20am%20a%20minimalist.%20The%20touchscreen%20contributes%20significantly%20to%20that%20premium%20feel%20when%20used.%20It%20blends%20seamlessly%20into%20the%20front%20panel.%20But%20when%20it's%20illuminated%2C%20it's%20bright%2C%20clear%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate.%20That%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20spacious%20basket%20and%20secure%2C%20makes%20this%20overall%20design%20polished%2C%20user-friendly%2C%20and%20incredibly%20thoughtful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229bd27f9b-4d43-48a4-96f6-20b200606e49%5C%22%3EIt%20does%20more%20than%20air%20fry%2C%20but%20air%20frying%20is%20still%20the%20reason%20to%20buy%20it.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cosori%20has%20multiple%20functions%20(dehydrate%2C%20proof%2C%20bake%2C%20roast%2C%20broil%2C%20and%20reheat)%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20good%20thing.%20I%20like%20an%20air%20fryer%20with%20extra%20functions%2C%20especially%20the%20reheat%20function%2C%20which%20I%20use%20often.%20Say%20you%20have%20a%20kid%20who%20doesn't%20eat%20dinner%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family%20due%20to%20sports%2C%20but%20still%20wants%20them%20to%20have%20hot%2C%20fresh%20food.%20The%20reheat%20function%20comes%20in%20clutch%20on%20such%20occasions%2C%20so%20everyone%20gets%20hot%20and%20crispy%20dinners%20no%20matter%20when%20they%20eat.%20I%20haven't%20tried%20the%20dehydrator%20function%20yet%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20wait%20to%20use%20it%20for%20tomatoes%20and%20stone%20fruit%20come%20summer%20abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259e0fbaa-1b41-48f1-a8bb-e2d043345628%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cleanup%5C%22%3ECleanup%20was%20straightforward%2C%20but%20treat%20the%20handle%20carefully.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20cosori%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3991fa36d7e6f260b78159%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThird-party%20reviewers%20have%20mentioned%20having%20issues%20with%20the%20release%20button%20over%20time.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Zyman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClean%20up%20was%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20parts%20of%20testing%20the%20TurboBlaze.%20Both%20the%20basket%20and%20the%20crisper%20plate%20are%20quick%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20even%20the%20greasiest%20foods%20leave%20minimal%20residue%2C%20since%20you%20can%20throw%20the%20basket%20into%20the%20dishwasher.%20My%20only%20concern%20is%20about%20the%20handle%20mechanism.%20During%20testing%2C%20it%20functioned%20normally%2C%20but%20some%20owners%20have%20reported%20issues%20with%20the%20release%20button%20over%20time.%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20failures%2C%20but%20that%20component%20is%20worth%20treating%20with%20care%20to%20maximize%20your%20appliance's%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22840f7ac2-3f82-4fe3-b44b-715b2db5c274%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Drawbacks%20and%20alternatives%5C%22%3EDrawbacks%20and%20alternatives%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20Instant%20Vortex%20and%20Beautiful%20air%20fryer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insi