insider.com%2F6a4297e4e218c3b62535ec8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20iconic%20movies%20and%20shows%20have%20been%20filmed%20in%20Utah.%3Cp%3EErica%20Finamore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20what%20makes%20Utah%20so%20visually%20striking%20is%20how%20familiar%20it%20already%20feels.%20For%20decades%2C%20filmmakers%20used%20the%20state's%20landscapes%20to%20define%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F15-beautiful-pictures-of-the-vast-american-west-2012-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elook%20of%20the%20American%20West%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMovies%20like%20%26quot%3BButch%20Cassidy%20and%20the%20Sundance%20Kid%26quot%3B%20used%20Utah's%20dramatic%20scenery%20as%20a%20backdrop%2C%20and%20towns%20like%20Kanab%20became%20production%20hubs%20for%20generations%20of%20Westerns.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKanab%20was%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Hollywood%26quot%3B%20because%20so%20many%20films%20were%20shot%20there%2C%20and%20the%20Once%20Upon%20a%20Time%20in%20America%20Museum%20still%20preserves%20that%20history%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20modern%20classics%20like%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20(seasons%20one%20through%20three)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthelma-and-louise-alternate-ending-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThelma%20%26amp%3B%20Louise%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20also%20filmed%20here%2C%20and%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20productions%20is%20already%20taking%20shape.%20Kevin%20Costner%20recently%20built%20a%20new%20film%20studio%20in%20St.%20George.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe5857e4-2a3d-4bea-a5a6-196f556d3fa6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20got%20ghost%20towns%20galore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22homestead%20from%20the%201850's%20in%20the%20Ghost%20Town%20of%20Grafton%2C%20Utah%20with%20buttes%20in%20background%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42963e360acd489560cfc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalking%20through%20some%20places%2C%20like%20Grafton%20Ghost%20Town%2C%20feels%20like%20being%20on%20a%20movie%20set.%3Cp%3Ewhammer121736%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUtah%20is%20home%20to%20more%20than%20140%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghost-towns-to-visit-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecognized%20ghost%20towns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20abandoned%20after%20failed%20farming%20settlements%2C%20flooding%2C%20or%20the%20collapse%20of%20mining%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20is%20Grafton%20Ghost%20Town%2C%20located%20just%20outside%20Zion%20National%20Park.%20Established%20in%201859%20by%20Mormon%20settlers%2C%20it%20later%20became%20known%20as%20a%20filming%20location%20for%20%26quot%3BButch%20Cassidy%20and%20the%20Sundance%20Kid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20town%20remains%20remarkably%20well-preserved%2C%20with%20its%201886%20schoolhouse%20and%20adobe%20homes%20sitting%20beneath%20towering%20red%20cliffs.%20Walking%20through%20it%20feels%20eerie%20and%20strangely%20emotional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20people%20who%20once%20built%20lives%20there%2C%20only%20to%20be%20driven%20out%20by%20the%20unpredictable%20flooding%20of%20the%20Virgin%20River%20and%20other%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247910813-b452-4b00-bbcd-bc8b779adcc6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20night%20sky%20can%20change%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20stayed%20with%20me%20most%20wasn't%20just%20the%20landscapes%3B%20it%20was%20the%20feeling%20of%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20forget%20how%20dark%20the%20night%20sky%20can%20actually%20get.%20In%20Utah%2C%20the%20stars%20felt%20impossibly%20bright%20and%20endless.%20Combined%20with%20the%20silence%2C%20the%20open%20roads%2C%20and%20the%20constant%20presence%20of%20nature%2C%20it%20created%20a%20sense%20of%20calm%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20I%20was%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20came%20home%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20be%20back%20with%20my%20family%2C%20but%20part%20of%20me%20still%20missed%20the%20red%20rocks%2C%20the%20endless%20horizons%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20that%20something%20extraordinary%20was%20waiting%20around%20every%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-state-visited-utah-frequent-traveler-tips-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782751217000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a429a37360acd489560cff5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-state-visited-utah-frequent-traveler-tips-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20visiting%2038%20states%20in%20the%20US%20during%20my%20travels%2C%20there's%20just%20one%20I%20can't%20stop%20thinking%20about%20for%20its%20scenery%2C%20history%2C%20and%20national%20parks%3A%20Utah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Erica%20Finamore)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22F1%20visa%20refusal%3A%20Former%20visa%20officer%20says%20Indians%20taught%20to%20memorize%20everything%2C%20rehearsed%20answers%20sound%20like%20lies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782750817000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132075384%2Cimgsize-149000.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ff1-visa-refusal-former-visa-officer-says-indians-taught-to-memorize-everything-rehearsed-answers-sound-like-lies%2Farticleshow%2F132075376.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2