n%3Cp%3ESanchita%20has%20observed%20similar%20changes%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20improvements%20in%20focus%20and%20sleep%20patterns.%20When%20parents%20swap%20sugar-loaded%20evening%20snacks%20with%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20fruit%20smoothies%2C%20kids%20are%20calmer%20at%20bedtime%20and%20more%20alert%20in%20school.%20The%20difference%20is%20visible%20within%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGovernment%E2%80%99s%20push%20on%20the%20millet%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20isn%E2%80%99t%20leaving%20this%20revival%20only%20to%20parents.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20The%20idea%3A%20fight%20malnutrition%20globally%20while%20supporting%20climate-resilient%20crops%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMid-Day%20meals%20in%20anganwadis%3A%20States%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Odisha%20now%20serve%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20malt%2C%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20jowar%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFarmer%20support%3A%20Incentives%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20and%20processing%20encourage%20rural%20economies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAwareness%20drives%3A%20Millet%20festivals%2C%20recipe%20competitions%2C%20and%20celebrity%20endorsements%20are%20changing%20perceptions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20a%20global%20conference%20hosted%20sessions%20on%20key%20millet-related%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20including%20promotion%20and%20awareness%20among%20producers%2C%20consumers%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%3B%20value%20chain%20development%3B%20health%20and%20nutrition%3B%20market%20linkages%3B%20and%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20nutrition%3A%20Building%20food%20relationships%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20both%20experts%20agree%3A%20food%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20forget%20the%20relationship%20children%20have%20with%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanchita.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20grow%20microgreens%20or%20help%20stir%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%2C%20they%20value%20food%20differently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20echoes%20this%2C%20drawing%20from%20Western%20practices%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20countries%2C%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20join%20in%20kitchens.%20Let%20them%20knead%20dough%2C%20cut%20veggies%2C%20or%20make%20pancake%20shapes.%20Even%20if%20the%20kitchen%20gets%20messy%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20likely%20to%20eat%20the%20food%20they%20helped%20make.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPlanting%20seeds%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildhood%20is%20fleeting%2C%20but%20its%20foundations%20last%20a%20lifetime.%20By%20the%20age%20of%20five%2C%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20brain%20is%20already%2090%25%20developed.%20The%20foods%20parents%20offer%20in%20these%20early%20years%20%E2%80%94%20say%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Einstead%20of%20instant%20noodles%2C%20microgreen%20salads%20instead%20of%20fries%20%E2%80%94%20quietly%20shape%20not%20just%20health%2C%20but%20focus%2C%20mood%2C%20and%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microgreens%20in%20food%20grade%20trays%20are%20grown%20in%20controlled%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2FAjay-growing-microgreens-in-racks-and-food-grade-trays-under-in-a-controlled-environment-1669988504-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-304882%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMicrogreens%20in%20food%20grade%20trays%20are%20grown%20in%20controlled%20environment.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20sums%20it%20up%3A%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20us%20today%20have%20autoimmune%20conditions.%20A%20lot%20of%20women%20deal%20with%20PCOS%20and%20hormonal%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20much%20of%20it%20linked%20to%20how%20we%20eat.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20give%20parents%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20stick%20to%20home-cooked%20meals.%20%3Cem%3EDal%3C%2Fem%3E-rice%20is%20great%2C%20but%20with%20gut%20health%20becoming%20such%20a%20challenge%2C%20we%20need%20to%20think%20beyond.%20What%20does%20our%20gut%20ask%20for%3F%20Fibre%20and%20variety.%20So%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E-rice%20or%20%3Cem%3Edal-roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20adding%20foods%20like%20moringa%20and%20millets%2C%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20antioxidants%2C%20can%20strengthen%20the%20gut%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20our%20immune%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20adds%3A%20%E2%80%9CKids%20today%20are%20smart.%20They%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20healthy%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20more%20attracted%20to%20packaged%20foods.%20Our%20job%20as%20parents%20is%20to%20make%20the%20good%20stuff%20just%20as%20fun%2C%20creative%2C%20and%20irresistible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESave%20this%20cheat%20sheet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20what%20to%20eat%20and%20what%20to%20include%20in%20your%20kid%E2%80%99s%20diet%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20overwhelming.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20perfect%20cheat%20sheet%20for%20parents%20to%20look%20up%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThree%20easy%20millet%20swaps%20for%20lunchboxes%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReplace%20white%20rice%20with%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20foxtail%20millet%20upma%20for%20a%20filling%20meal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwap%20maida-based%20wraps%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412561%2Fmillets-summer-cooling-jowar-foxtail-ragi-temperature-diet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejowar%20or%20bajra%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stuffed%20with%20veggies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETry%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20millet%20cookies%20as%20tiffin%20treats%20instead%20of%20packaged%20biscuits.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20quickest%20microgreen%20uses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESprinkle%20on%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20a%20nutrient%20boost.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMix%20into%20omelettes%20or%20scrambled%20eggs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdd%20as%20a%20topping%20for%20soups%20or%20noodles.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBlend%20a%20handful%20into%20smoothies%20or%20chutneys.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20instead%20of%20coriander%20for%20a%20fresh%20garnish.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFour%20label-check%20rules%20for%20packaged%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELook%20at%20the%20first%203%20ingredients.%20If%20sugar%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20or%20palm%20oil%20lead%20the%20list%2C%20skip%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChoose%20products%20with%20less%20than%205%20g%20of%20sugar%20per%20serving.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrefer%20snacks%20with%20whole%20grains%2C%20nuts%2C%20or%20seeds%20listed%20upfront.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoid%20items%20with%20too%20many%20unpronounceable%20additives%3B%20simple%20is%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20handful%20of%20microgreens%20on%20a%20sandwich%20to%20a%20weekly%20batch%20of%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20laddoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20small%20steps%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20For%20India%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrition%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20reconnecting%20with%20roots%2C%20celebrating%20resilience%2C%20and%20giving%20our%20children%20the%20tools%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757065097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fmicrogreens_11zon-1756194438.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parents%20across%20India%20are%20rethinking%20school%20tiffins%20by%20replacing%20packaged%20snacks%20with%20nutrient-rich%20millets%20and%20microgreens.%20Easy%20to%20grow%20and%20cook%2C%20these%20superfoods%20boost%20children%E2%80%99s%20focus%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20immunity%20%E2%80%94%20making%20them%20fun%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20practical%20lunchbox%20staples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496778%2Fmillets-microgreens-pack-kids-healthy-lunchbox-ideas-nutrition-superfood%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Couple%E2%80%99s%20Biofortified%20Seeds%20Venture%20Is%20Transforming%2015000%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Lives%20With%20Rs%2010%20Cr%20Turnover%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20September%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20three%20years%20back%2C%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20had%20not%20heard%20about%20biofortified%20seeds%20%E2%80%93%20seeds%20that%20have%20been%20bred%20to%20have%20higher%20levels%20of%20certain%20nutrients%20like%20iron%20and%20zinc.%20The%20farmer%20has%20been%20successfully%20growing%20wheat%20on%20his%205.5-acre%20landholding%20using%20these%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20switch%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%20was%20prompted%20by%20his%20concerns%20over%20the%20rampant%20use%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20which%20not%20only%20harm%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20pose%20health%20risks%20to%20consumers.%20He%20chose%20to%20invest%20in%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20zinc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496772%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20outcomes%20of%20Sukhwinder%E2%80%99s%20adoption%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20is%20the%20improvement%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20children%20find%20the%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chapati)%20made%20from%20the%20wheat%20grown%20with%20biofortified%20seeds%20tastier.%20This%20has%20not%20only%20enhanced%20the%20taste%20of%20my%20produce%20but%20also%20ensured%20that%20my%20children%20consume%20safe%20and%20nutritious%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2049-year-old%20resident%20of%20Bambhera%20village%2C%20Sitapur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prateek%20and%20Aishwarya%20studying%20plants%20with%20farmers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrateek%20and%20Aishwarya%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20with%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20zinc%2C%20iron%2C%20manganese%2C%20boron%2C%20and%20copper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20has%20also%20reduced%20his%20input%20costs%20by%20reducing%20his%20dependency%20on%20urea%20fertiliser.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20to%20add%20three%20rags%20of%20urea%20on%20one%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20now%20I%20only%20have%20to%20add%20as%20little%20as%20half%20a%20rag%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukhwinder%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20yield%20per%20acre%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower%20compared%20to%20conventional%20seeds%2C%20the%20overall%20benefits%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326709%2Fcultyvate-agri-tech-solution-helps-paddy-farmers-reduce-water-waste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduced%20input%20costs%20and%20improved%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20far%20outweigh%20any%20minor%20differences%20in%20productivity.%20Besides%2C%20I%20am%20earning%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20instead%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20rates%20for%20regular%20wheat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Sukhwinder%2C%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20thanks%20to%20Aishwarya%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%2C%20who%20are%20promoting%20innovative%20and%20eco-friendly%20farming%20methods%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20food%20we%20eat%20daily%20nutritious%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20completing%20higher%20studies%20and%20gaining%20entrepreneurship%20training%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Prateek%20felt%20a%20strong%20calling%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20in%20his%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20advised%20to%20venture%20into%20more%20developed%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat%20for%20ease%20of%20business%2C%20he%20strived%20to%20focus%20on%20central%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20regions%20that%20still%20required%20substantial%20advancement%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20for%20the%20corporate%20world%20for%20a%20year%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20his%20ancestral%20village%20in%20Sitapur%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Aishwarya%2C%20who%20is%20an%20alumna%20of%20IHM%20Bombay%20where%20she%20studied%20food%20sciences%20and%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20out%20to%20live%20out%20of%20an%20agri-warehouse.%20This%20is%20where%20they%20learnt%20more%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342901%2Ffarmer-income-success-lcb-fertilizers-biofertiliser-navyakosh-akshay-shrivastav-iit-kanpur-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRural%20visits%20are%20close%20to%20our%20hearts.%20We%20love%20spending%20time%20in%20villages%2C%20cooking%20by%20a%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20chulha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(firewood%20stove)%2C%20and%20sharing%20stories%20with%20farmers.%20I%20also%20grew%20up%20eating%20farm%20produce%20that%20was%20sent%20to%20us%20from%20our%20village%20to%20our%20home%20in%20Lucknow.%20These%20experiences%20fuel%20our%20passion%20for%20our%20startup%20and%20our%20commitment%20to%20improving%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20farming%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20he%20observed%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20farmers%20toil%20day%20and%20night%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20it%20lacks%20sufficient%20nutritional%20content.%20India%20faces%20severe%20micronutrient%20deficiencies%20due%20to%20essential%20nutrients%20lacking%20in%20crop%20outputs%2C%20leading%20to%20health%20issues%20like%20anaemia%20and%20stunted%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20At%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-2-1725601012-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20At%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%205%20(2019-21)%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1795421%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E57%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20women%20aged%2015-49%20in%20India%20are%20anaemic%20whereas%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1806601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E35.5%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20are%20stunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20untapped%20power%20in%20the%20food%20we%20consume%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20our%20diet%20is%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20rice.%20Looking%20at%20the%20anaemia%20and%20stunting%20data%20of%20our%20country%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20do%20not%20get%20enough%20nutrients%20from%20the%20food%20we%20eat.%20I%20strongly%20believe%20that%20nutrition%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20right%20for%20us%20all%20Indians.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20everyone%20deserves%20access%20to%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20a%20privilege%20for%20a%20few.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20improve%20crop%20nutrition%20naturally%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20of%20crops%20such%20as%20maize%2C%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296561%2Fmahalingam-govindaraj-scientist-develops-first-biofortified-pearl-millet-bajra-wins-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinger%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20zinc%2C%20iron%2C%20manganese%2C%20boron%2C%20and%20copper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20Greenday%20in%20January%202020%2C%20aiming%20to%20bring%20systemic%20innovation%20and%20enhance%20crop%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImproving%20nutritional%20value%20through%20biofortification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%20of%20Greenday%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20was%20simple%20yet%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20nutritional%20quality%20of%20crops%20while%20empowering%20farmers%20economically.%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20were%20not%20only%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20income%20through%20premium%20pricing%20but%20also%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20addressing%20widespread%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342444%2Fias-officer-avi-prasad-community-programme-to-fight-malnutrition-katni-madhya-pradesh-donate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissues%20of%20malnutrition%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20developed%20through%20crossbreeding%20for%20nutritional%20benefits%20and%20climate%20resilience%2C%20showed%20promising%20results%20in%20increasing%20essential%20nutrient%20levels%20by%20up%20to%2080%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20introducing%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20enrich%20the%20soil%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20seeds%20enabled%20plants%20to%20absorb%20more%20nutrients%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20significantly%20higher%20nutritional%20content%20in%20the%20harvested%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20baseline%20levels%20of%20zinc%20in%20the%20traditional%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20around%2028%20parts%20per%20million%20whereas%2C%20it%20is%2045%20parts%20per%20million%20in%20the%20newer%20bio%20fortified%20seeds.%20We%20also%20add%20a%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20the%20soil%20which%20helps%20mobilise%20the%20naturally%20available%20zinc%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20roots.%20This%20increases%20zinc%20base%20levels%20to%2050-55%20parts%20per%20million%20%E2%80%93%20an%20increment%20of%20about%2080%20percent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20every%20seed%20will%20have%20its%20own%20benefits%20and%20drawbacks.%20These%20seeds%20give%20almost%2080%20percent%20more%20nutritional%20value%20but%20farmers%20may%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20of%204%20to%205%20percent%20in%20yield.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349986%2Fprabhat-kumar-sumarth-ngo-bihar-horticulture-training-for-farmers-double-income-cash-crops%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremium%20rates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20such%20produce%20covers%20up%20the%20yield%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborations%20with%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20across%20regions%20like%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Basti%2C%20Gonda%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20and%20others%2C%20the%20initiative%20not%20only%20promoted%20the%20adoption%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20but%20also%20provided%20holistic%20services%20ranging%20from%20soil%20analysis%20to%20crop%20selection%20in%20order%20to%20boost%20crop%20nutrient%20content%20naturally.%20Greenday%20has%20achieved%20an%20annual%C2%A0turnover%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20impact%20created%20by%20their%20startup%2C%20Aishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20spending%202.5%20years%20in%20Sitapur%20closely%20working%20with%20farmers%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%20in%20something%20as%20small%20as%20a%20seed.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20massive%20impact%20by%20working%20for%20our%20farmers.%20Seeing%20their%20dedication%20first%20hand%20has%20been%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experience.%20Their%20hard%20work%20fuels%20our%20passion%20to%20turn%20our%20brand%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20improves%20health%20but%20also%20supports%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20All%20photos%3A%20Greenday.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757059200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496772%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow-based%20Aishwarya%20Bhatnagar%20and%20Prateek%20Rastogi%20run%20Greenday%20to%20promote%20innovative%20farming%20methods%20and%20biofortified%20seeds%20that%20benefit%20both%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496772%2Fgreenday-biofortified-seeds-lucknow-farmer-income-nutrition%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20%E2%80%98Sadya%E2%80%99%20Feast%3A%20Onam%20Festival%20Traditions%2C%20Dances%20%26amp%3B%20Boat%20Races%20You%20Must%20See%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnam%20is%20often%20celebrated%20through%20its%20grandest%20highlight%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Onam%20%3Cem%3ESadya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20lavish%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F491736%2Fonam-2025-kerala-sadhya-authentic-recipes-by-top-chefs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetarian%20feast%20served%20on%20banana%20leaves%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20enjoyed%20with%20family%20and%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20the%20kitchens%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3ESadya%3C%2Fem%3E%20takes%20centre%20stage%20lies%20an%20equally%20vibrant%20world%20of%20rituals%2C%20performances%2C%20and%20tradition